  ('Skala Expert Avocado Hair Treatment Conditioning Cream', 'skala-expert-avocado-hair-treatment-conditioning-cream', 'Online shopping for SKALA. Trusted Shipping to Riyadh, Jeddah and all KSA ✓ Great Prices ✓ Secure Shopping ✓ 100% Contactless ✓ Easy Free Returns ✓ Cash on Delivery. Shop Now', 'Online shopping for SKALA. Trusted Shipping to Riyadh, Jeddah and all KSA ✓ Great Prices ✓ Secure Shopping ✓ 100% Contactless ✓ Easy Free Re…', 7.5, NULL, 'BHD', '["https://f.nooncdn.com/p/pzsku/Z06B94E2DD1AF11C5B752Z/45/1746214629/8e074253-4f0b-408a-90ce-8714c7719fe7.jpg?width=1200"]'::jsonb, (select id from public.categories where slug = 'hair-scalp-treatments'), (select id from public.brands where slug = 'skala'), 4, 1, 0, true, false, true, ARRAY['hair', 'care', 'scalp', 'treatments', 'masks']::text[]),
  ('Keratin Shampoo and Conditioner Contain Silk Worm Protein and Buriti Oil and Cupuacu Butter For Long Lasting Treatment Result, Give the Hair shiny and Healthy Look Made In Brazil 250ml x 2', 'keratin-shampoo-and-conditioner-contain-silk-worm-protein-and-buriti-o', '1- PROLIFE INTERNATIONAL AFTERCARE SHAMPOO In addition to cleaning the hair, it also moistures it. The beauty of the strands will be highlighted by this product, which has an extremely mild and creamy base. It cleans the hair but does not dry it. The active ingredients present in its formulation prolong the treatment’s durability in the hair. 2- PROLIFE INTERNATIONAL AFTER CARE CONDITIONER The features in its formula, are conditioning agents that provide an extra shine to the hair. intensively nourishes and conditions the hair strands during combing, increasing and prolonging the effects of straightening.', '1- PROLIFE INTERNATIONAL AFTERCARE SHAMPOO In addition to cleaning the hair, it also moistures it.', 5.9, NULL, 'BHD', '["https://f.nooncdn.com/p/pzsku/ZCC4D488F0A79BE9250A4Z/45/1765253301/59abee48-f434-46e2-8288-0bbb1fae84f9.jpg?width=1200"]'::jsonb, (select id from public.categories where slug = 'hair-scalp-treatments'), (select id from public.brands where slug = 'prolife-international'), 4.8, 7, 0, true, false, true, ARRAY['hair', 'care', 'scalp', 'treatments', 'curls', 'straightening']::text[]),
  ('Professional 2200W Ionic Hair Dryer - High Speed Quiet Blow Dryer with 3 Heat & 2 Speed Settings, Cool Shot, Concentrator Nozzle & Hanging Hook - Perfect for Salon & Home Styling Black', 'professional-2200w-ionic-hair-dryer-high-speed-quiet-blow-dryer-with-3', '1. GEEPAS 2200 WATT POWER HAIR DRYER - Suits all your hair styling needs and gives professional, long-lasting results. The size of this hair dryer is 23.7x9x28.7cm. 2. BRINGING YOU SALON-QUALITY HAIR AT HOME! - Geepas understands how great hair gives you the confidence to walk taller every day. Hair will be glossy and frizz-free thanks to the anti-static Ionic action technology. With variable heat and speed settings, you can tailor your blow-dry to your hair type. It saves significantly more energy than other heat settings. Finish with the Cool Shot button for ultra-glossy tresses and a style that stays in place all day and night. 3. IONIC ACTION TECHNOLOGY - It helps to tighten the hair cuticles and creates a smooth frizz-free finish giving a long-lasting result with perfectly straight and dry hair. It works for all types of hair, and the styles are lasting. 4. COOL SHOT FUNCTION - This hair dryer has a cool shot button. Its name is self-explanatory as it gives a cool blow to the hair and is very useful for setting a hairstyle in place. This makes your hairstyle last longer as it does not get disturbed easily. 5. POWERFUL HAIRDRYER AND PROFESSIONAL CONCENTRATOR - This hair dryer may look small but can handle all styling routines with ease. It is easy to use and gives a professional touch. It carefully removes the water while protecting the hair from heat giving a controlled and concentrated style that remains still day and night.', '1. GEEPAS 2200 WATT POWER HAIR DRYER - Suits all your hair styling needs and gives professional, long-lasting results.', 9.9, NULL, 'BHD', '["https://f.nooncdn.com/p/pzsku/ZFC9CC0748A959757C856Z/45/_/1779706059/08db3719-29c0-491f-b2eb-9120f3b87102.jpg?width=1200","https://f.n