  ('Hair Mask With Protein And Argan Oil 3 in 1 By Cosmo1000 ml', 'hair-mask-with-protein-and-argan-oil-3-in-1-by-cosmo1000-ml', 'Protein: Protein is known as the building block of hair, as it helps strengthen hair and give it a natural shine. Argan Oil: Argan oil is known as the “gold of the desert” due to its many benefits for hair. It is rich in vitamin E and antioxidants, which help moisturize, soften and protect hair from damage. Vitamin E: Vitamin E is a powerful antioxidant that helps protect hair from damage caused by free radicals. Antioxidants: Antioxidants help protect hair from damage caused by environmental factors such as sunlight and pollution.', 'Protein: Protein is known as the building block of hair, as it helps strengthen hair and give it a natural shine.', 2.4, NULL, 'BHD', '["https://f.nooncdn.com/p/pzsku/Z8F538A0E42767FE1C899Z/45/_/1724850893/bd1b4416-d526-4d7e-8618-80057baadd34.jpg?width=1200"]'::jsonb, (select id from public.categories where slug = 'hair-scalp-treatments'), (select id from public.brands where slug = 'cosmo'), 4.2, 11, 0, true, false, true, ARRAY['hair', 'care', 'scalp', 'treatments', 'masks']::text[]),
