  ('Classic Black EDT For Men 100ml', 'classic-black-edt-for-men-100ml', 'About the product: Classic Black by Jaguar is a Oriental Fougere fragrance for men. Classic Black was launched in 2009. The nose behind this fragrance is Dominique Preyssas. Top notes are Granny Smith apple, Bitter Orange and Mandarin Orange; middle notes are Tea, Sea water, Geranium, Nutmeg and Cardamom; base notes are White Musk, Virginia Cedar, Tonka Bean, Vetiver, Sandalwood and oak moss. About the brand: Jaguar is popular amongst many well-known celebrities. The first Jaguar perfume was created in 1986. Like the car, it is of high quality, original, and full of power and luxury. Jaguar fragrance is not just produced for men but women too who like to treat themselves and allow themselves to be dominated by a unique sensuality. Ingredients: Alcohol, Parfum (Fragrance), Aqua (Water), Limonene, Ethylhexyl Methoxycinnamate, Diethylamino, Hydroxybenzoyl Hexylbenzoate, Citral, Cinnamal, Linlool, Bht. How to use: Spray on pulse points: behind the ears and on your wrists.', 'Classic Black by Jaguar is a Oriental Fougere fragrance for men. Classic Black was launched in 2009.', 4.445, NULL, 'BHD', '["https://f.nooncdn.com/p/pzsku/Z2A7172342215DE5FA7D5Z/45/_/1779094781/4d45f60b-e9f3-4702-aa35-2d3447bf5940.jpg?width=1200","https://f.nooncdn.com/p/pzsku/Z2A7172342215DE5FA7D5Z/45/_/1779094781/80f970e6-9db9-4070-8a6d-c1df7848aa76.jpg?width=1200","https://f.nooncdn.com/p/pzsku/Z2A7172342215DE5FA7D5Z/45/_/1779094781/55442024-51b5-4e06-a926-f84c0b27ffd4.jpg?width=1200","https://f.nooncdn.com/p/pzsku/Z2A7172342215DE5FA7D5Z/45/_/1779094782/efee7cc3-2f36-4f3b-92b4-af5cd4a0ee50.jpg?width=1200"]'::jsonb, (select id from public.categories where slug = 'fragrance'), (select id from public.brands where slug = 'jaguar'), 4.1, 8720, 0, true, false, true, ARRAY['fragrance']::text[]),
  ('Khamrah Unisex Eau De Parfum by Lattafa 100ml', 'khamrah-unisex-eau-de-parfum-by-lattafa-100ml', 'Online shopping for Lattafa. Trusted Shipping to Riyadh, Jeddah and all KSA ✓ Great Prices ✓ Secure Shopping ✓ 100% Contactless ✓ Easy Free Returns ✓ Cash on Delivery. Shop Now', 'Online shopping for Lattafa. Trusted Shipping to Riyadh, Jeddah and all KSA ✓ Great Prices ✓ Secure Shopping ✓ 100% Contactless ✓ Easy Free…', 8.75, NULL, 'BHD', '["https://f.nooncdn.com/p/pzsku/ZF23DE5EC51560ADE2D7EZ/45/1765448761/ed471666-5186-49bf-951c-1324ddabc83c.jpg?width=1200","https://f.nooncdn.com/p/pzsku/ZF23DE5EC51560ADE2D7EZ/45/1748345898/d89102f7-fc15-4b19-a050-bf8f544e4765.jpg?width=1200","https://f.nooncdn.com/p/pzsku/ZF23DE5EC51560ADE2D7EZ/45/1748345897/c7510f27-b563-40a4-86d1-df69689c7ed9.jpg?width=1200","https://f.nooncdn.com/p/pzsku/ZF23DE5EC51560ADE2D7EZ/45/1748345898/21960670-4395-44fe-8c36-4b2528a81e8c.jpg?width=1200"]'::jsonb, (select id from public.categories where slug = 'eau-de-parfum'), (select id from public.brands where slug = 'lattafa'), 4.4, 7609, 0, true, false, true, ARRAY['fragrance', 'eau', 'parfum']::text[]),
  ('MISK COLLECTION (3GM X 6 PCS)', 'misk-collection-3gm-x-6-pcs', 'Introducing the Misk Collection: a curated selection of 6 opulent perfume oil fragrances from Ajmal''s esteemed collection. This exquisite range features Ajmal''s Musk Silk, Ajmal Misk Al Arosah, Misk Ehsaas, Misk Rumman, Misk Powder and Ajmal Misk Pistachio. Each fragrance is a masterpiece from our Misk range Series, carefully crafted to evoke emotions and leave a lasting impression. The Misk Collection is an ideal choice for gifting someone special, and its versatility makes it suitable for all occasions', 'Introducing the Misk Collection: a curated selection of 6 opulent perfume oil fragrances from Ajmal''s esteemed collection.', 15.525, NULL, 'BHD', '["https://f.nooncdn.com/p/pzsku/ZC4217BFF547D894BF0E4Z/45/_/1739973102/730954d3-902c-47c0-b22d-c88e2d0765ea.jpg?width=1200","https://f.nooncdn.com/p/pzsku/ZC4217BFF547D894BF0E4Z/45/_/1739973103/157d0c66-0b1a-479d-a642-9f9cc20587cf.jpg?width=1200","https://f.nooncdn.com/p/pzsku/ZC4217BFF547D894BF0E4Z/45/_/1739973108/ce9eaabf-e575-4360-955d-08991e5676d4.jpg?width=1200"]'::jsonb, (select id from public.categories where slug = 'fragrance-gift-sets'), (select id from public.brands where slug = 'ajmal'), 4.6, 209, 0, true, false, true, ARRAY['fragrance', 'gift', 'sets']::text[]),
  ('SUGAR LEMON SORBET EDP 100ML', 'sugar-lemon-sorbet-edp-100ml', 'Arabiyat Sugar Lemon Sorbet Eau de Parfum is a refreshing gourmand fragrance that captures the joyful essence of a frozen citrus dessert. It opens with vibrant lemon and citrus zest, delivering a crisp and energizing start that feels bright and cheerful. As the scent develops, a sweet lemon sorbet accord emerges in the heart, blending freshness with a soft sugary sweetness that feels clean and addictive. The fragrance gently dries down into a smooth base of vanilla and musk with light woods, giving it warmth, balance, and lasting appeal. Perfect for everyday wear, especially in warm weather, this fragrance is ideal for those who love fresh yet sweet citrus scents.', 'Arabiyat Sugar Lemon Sorbet Eau de Parfum is a refreshing gourmand fragrance that captures the joyful essence of a frozen citrus dessert.', 11.57, NULL, 'BHD', '["https://f.nooncdn.com/p/pzsku/ZE185E93446D95D0D8875Z/45/_/1773644233/3fca5968-6828-4f14-aa5d-026ec690d443.jpg?width=1200","https://f.nooncdn.com/p/pzsku/ZE185E93446D95D0D8875Z/45/_/1773644233/b646d0c7-9741-40f1-8128-275639f94f7c.jpg?width=1200","https://f.nooncdn.com/p/pzsku/ZE185E93446D95D0D8875Z/45/_/1773644233/b5b71812-37d5-4652-a209-a474271da677.jpg?width=1200"]'::jsonb, (select id from public.categories where slug = 'eau-de-parfum'), (select id from public.brands where slug = 'arabiyat'), 5, 2, 0, true, false, true, ARRAY['fragrance', 'eau', 'parfum']::text[]),
  ('SUGAR STRAWBERRY TRES LECHES EDP 100ML', 'sugar-strawberry-tres-leches-edp-100ml', 'Arabiyat Sugar Strawberry Tres Leches Eau de Parfum is a deliciously indulgent gourmand fragrance inspired by the beloved creamy dessert. It begins with fresh strawberry sweetness that feels vibrant and playful, instantly drawing attention. As the scent develops, the heart unveils creamy strawberry and tres leches cake accords blended with smooth milk notes, creating a rich, soft, and comforting character. The fragrance dries down into a warm base of vanilla, musk, and light woods, enhancing longevity while maintaining a gentle sweetness. Perfect for everyday wear or cozy moments, this fragrance is ideal for lovers of fruity, creamy, and dessert-inspired perfumes.', 'Arabiyat Sugar Strawberry Tres Leches Eau de Parfum is a deliciously indulgent gourmand fragrance inspired by the beloved creamy dessert.', 11.57, NULL, 'BHD', '["https://f.nooncdn.com/p/pzsku/Z25FFE990D2661098A05DZ/45/_/1773644233/8bcdcbc0-c03a-466c-a70a-02fb7d353d16.jpg?width=1200","https://f.nooncdn.com/p/pzsku/Z25FFE990D2661098A05DZ/45/_/1773644233/98ea00af-26ae-4de7-901f-c14620dd98f0.jpg?width=1200","https://f.nooncdn.com/p/pzsku/Z25FFE990D2661098A05DZ/45/_/1773644233/832471d0-ba39-409c-8162-6291c04f2340.jpg?width=1200"]'::jsonb, (select id from public.categories where slug = 'eau-de-parfum'), (select id from public.brands where slug = 'arabiyat'), 5, 1, 0, true, false, true, ARRAY['fragrance', 'eau', 'parfum']::text[]),
  ('AFNAN Supremacy Collector''s Edition Eau De Parfum for Men, 100 ML', 'afnan-supremacy-collector-s-edition-eau-de-parfum-for-men-100-ml', 'Afnan Supremacy Collector''s Edition for Men is a statement fragrance that exudes masculinity and sophistication. It features a dynamic blend of citrus, aromatic spices, herbs, and an intense base of amber and musk. This scent is crafted for men who desire an unforgettable and long-lasting olfactory experience.', 'Afnan Supremacy Collector''s Edition for Men is a statement fragrance that exudes masculinity and sophistication.', 18.735, NULL, 'BHD', '["https://f.nooncdn.com/p/pzsku/ZDBE6518F223CA939280EZ/45/_/1775743355/9c6848b3-281d-421a-9fc5-55a669a3f781.jpg?width=1200","https://f.nooncdn.com/p/pzsku/ZDBE6518F223CA939280EZ/45/_/1775709339/f805a318-cca1-4267-947d-0b1a59edc9a1.jpg?width=1200","https://f.nooncdn.com/p/pzsku/ZDBE6518F223CA939280EZ/45/_/1775709339/813ba42e-b3f4-4552-9f0c-cc705fa834ac.jpg?width=1200","https://f.nooncdn.com/p/pzsku/ZDBE6518F223CA939280EZ/45/_/1775709339/729ac0b6-877e-48e6-9094-8956e2642928.jpg?width=1200"]'::jsonb, (select id from public.categories where slug = 'eau-de-parfum'), (select id from public.brands where slug = 'afnan'), 4.6, 855, 0, true, false, true, ARRAY['fragrance', 'eau', 'parfum']::text[]),
  ('Yara EDP For Women 100ml', 'yara-edp-for-women-100ml', 'Yara by Lattafa Perfumes is a Amber Vanilla fragrance for women. Yara was launched in 2020. Top notes are Orchid, Heliotrope and Tangerine; middle notes are Gourmand Accord and Tropical Fruits; base notes are Vanilla, Musk and Sandalwood.', 'Yara by Lattafa Perfumes is a Amber Vanilla fragrance for women. Yara was launched in 2020.', 6.005, NULL, 'BHD', '["https://f.nooncdn.com/p/pnsku/N52261837A/45/_/1753860178/97a92f5e-f37e-4742-86fc-edb16678e795.jpg?width=1200","https://f.nooncdn.com/p/pnsku/N52261837A/45/_/1753860095/80704d45-683e-4bb0-91f4-b13fb249faff.jpg?width=1200","https://f.nooncdn.com/p/pnsku/N52261837A/45/_/1753860096/5429c38d-8de3-4159-942b-55bf3f456b65.jpg?width=1200","https://f.nooncdn.com/p/pnsku/N52261837A/45/_/1753860104/44e4b7be-d0a9-45c8-a6f1-dafcf2db7eb3.jpg?width=1200"]'::jsonb, (select id from public.categories where slug = 'eau-de-parfum'), (select id from public.brands where slug = 'lattafa'), 4.5, 4124, 0, true, false, true, ARRAY['fragrance', 'eau', 'parfum']::text[]),
  ('Musk Concentrate Spray EDC 59ml', 'musk-concentrate-spray-edc-59ml', 'About the product: It is designed by the house of Jovan in 1972, JOVAN MUSK is classified as a luxurious, gentle, floral fragrance. This feminine scent possesses a blend of light musk and delicate florals. It is recommended for romantic wear. Jovan Musk is a luxury fragrance for women to complement your sporty-elegant style and pleasantly refresh you. Just a few drops of this perfume will make you incredibly self-confident! Musk emphasizes your feminity and mysteriousness for a long time. About the brand: Jovan fragrances were made in collaboration with perfumers Murray Moscona, Domitille Michalon Bertier and Nadège Le Garlantezec. Ingredients: Alcohol Denat., Aqua/Water, Parfum/Fragrance, Ethylhexyl Methoxycinnamate, Benzyl Benzoate, Benzophenone-3, Ethylhexyl Salicylate, Amyl Cinnamal, Butyl Methoxydibenzoylmethane, Alpha-isomethyl Ionone, Coumarin, Hydroxycitronellal, Linalool, Hexyl Cinnamal, Propylene Glycol, Benzyl Alcohol, Cinnamyl Alcohol, Isoeugenol, Geraniol, Evernia Prunastri, Acrylates/Octylacrylamide Copolymer, Bht, Hydrolyzed Jojoba Esters, Fd&c Yellow No. 5 (Ci 19140), Fd&c Red No. 4 (Ci 14700). How to use: Spray on pulse points around the body to increase the longevity of the fragrance.', 'It is designed by the house of Jovan in 1972, JOVAN MUSK is classified as a luxurious, gentle, floral fragrance.', 2.095, NULL, 'BHD', '["https://f.nooncdn.com/p/pzsku/Z925B20FE8EBA666734A5Z/45/_/1776947388/0d2820f4-d996-467c-b067-988c67aa13fa.jpg?width=1200","https://f.nooncdn.com/p/pzsku/Z925B20FE8EBA666734A5Z/45/_/1776947388/830c6af8-d01f-4e8b-a1fa-047c91225d86.jpg?width=1200","https://f.nooncdn.com/p/pzsku/Z925B20FE8EBA666734A5Z/45/_/1776947388/ebb74ddc-fc20-4e20-9b8a-ba8ca6544294.jpg?width=1200"]'::jsonb, (select id from public.categories where slug = 'fragrance'), (select id from public.brands where slug = 'jovan'), 4, 4780, 0, true, false, true, ARRAY['fragrance']::text[]),
  ('Black Secret Classic Perfume 100 Ml', 'black-secret-classic-perfume-100-ml', 'A composition that has its own magic of berries, jasmine and the softness of vanilla.', 'A composition that has its own magic of berries, jasmine and the softness of vanilla.', 6.9, NULL, 'BHD', '["https://f.nooncdn.com/p/pzsku/ZEEE626CA60D31BF1D2F5Z/45/1765448753/ed659ab9-0aa6-4db4-9e82-4909da192db7.jpg?width=1200","https://f.nooncdn.com/p/pzsku/ZEEE626CA60D31BF1D2F5Z/45/1754313728/7ebfffd9-0195-4fcf-9eb5-3fbfeb1cbb78.jpg?width=1200","https://f.nooncdn.com/p/pzsku/ZEEE626CA60D31BF1D2F5Z/45/1754313727/3a7bf8fe-244e-4130-a5cf-10df95565492.jpg?width=1200"]'::jsonb, (select id from public.categories where slug = 'eau-de-parfum'), (select id from public.brands where slug = 'al-majed-oud'), 4.3, 1532, 0, true, false, true, ARRAY['fragrance', 'eau', 'parfum']::text[]),
  ('Paradiso EDP 75ml', 'paradiso-edp-75ml', 'About the product: Paradiso is the key to a parallel world embraced by a secret garden in a magnificent villa nestled on the coast of the Mediterranean Sea. A tantalising prelude of crisp citrus notes blend with those of warm exotic bergamot and sweet mandarin. A fresh and sparkling head gives way to a subtle heart of wild jasmine. The base note of the fragrance boasts a rich and delicate accord of cypress, oleander and Mediterranean pine trees. A refined accord of Italian aromas extend and intensify the hypnotic effect of the jasmine generating a persistent woody base note. Made in France. About the brand: Made in France. Today, the brand is sold in more than 50 countries worldwide, and the name Cavalli is synonymous with a glamorous Italian lifestyle. The Cavalli brand offering includes menswear, underwear, accessories, and perfume. Ingredients: Alcohol Denat, Parfum/fragrance, Aqua/water/eau, Ethylhexyl Methoxycinnamate, Hydroxycitronellal, Butylphenyl Methylpropional, Benzyl Salicylate, Benzophenone-3, Ethylhexyl Salicylate, Limonene, Butyl Methoxydibenzoylmethane, Citronellol, Coumarin, Linalool, Bht, Hexyl Cinnamal, Farnesol, Isoeugenol, Methyl 2-octynoate, Propylene Glycol, Geraniol, Benzyl Benzoate, Benzyl Alcohol, Disodium Edta, Acrylates/octylacrylamide Copolymer, Hydrolyzed Jojoba Esters, Fd&c Yellow N°5 (Ci 19140), Fd&c Yellow N°6 (Ci 15985), Fd&c Red N°4 (Ci 14700). How to use: Spray on pulse points: behind the ears and on your wrists.', 'Paradiso is the key to a parallel world embraced by a secret garden in a magnificent villa nestled on the coast of the Mediterranean Sea.', 11.695, NULL, 'BHD', '["https://f.nooncdn.com/p/pzsku/Z7EB860432F99C45FA958Z/45/_/1778591215/2f3d24e3-111d-4323-ac0a-a9032ad1cce2.jpg?width=1200","https://f.nooncdn.com/p/pzsku/Z7EB860432F99C45FA958Z/45/_/1778591215/a3aaa58a-8f4d-4014-9fea-663b5b8f8064.jpg?width=1200","https://f.nooncdn.com/p/pzsku/Z7EB860432F99C45FA958Z/45/_/1778591215/d1748b14-050b-4cbf-8aca-184907ec32d2.jpg?width=1200","https://f.nooncdn.com/p/pzsku/Z7EB860432F99C45FA958Z/45/_/1778591215/a4df3de7-36b1-42a9-9098-1c7888a382a3.jpg?width=1200"]'::jsonb, (select id from public.categories where slug = 'fragrance'), (select id from public.brands where slug = 'roberto-cavalli'), 0, 0, 0, true, false, true, ARRAY['fragrance']::text[]),
  ('Menhood The Baller- Fresh Spray for Men Private Parts | Intimate Perfume | All Day Fresh| Prevents Itching, Sweating and Irritation Down There | 100 ML (Fragrance - Vanilla)', 'menhood-the-baller-fresh-spray-for-men-private-parts-intimate-perfume', 'Stay fresh, confident, and irritation-free all day with MENHOOD The Baller Intimate Hygiene Spray for Men—a premium men''s intimate hygiene spray designed for complete below-the-waist freshness. Specially crafted for men’s sensitive areas, this advanced ball spray for men delivers powerful protection against sweat and bad smell. Acting as an effective anti-odour spray for men, it helps keep the men''s private area clean, dry, and comfortable throughout the day. Enriched with natural tea tree oil and eucalyptus extract, this organic intimate spray for men provides a cooling, soothing sensation that helps reduce irritation, redness, and unwanted odour. It''s lightweight, non-sticky mist dries quickly and forms a breathable protective layer, making it an ideal men''s private part spray for daily use. Whether you’re heading to the gym, going to work, or stepping out for the evening, just a few spritzes ensure long-lasting freshness and confidence. MENHOOD The Baller Spray is 100% organic, vegan, and cruelty-free, free from parabens, dyes, and harsh chemicals. Safe for all skin types—including sensitive skin—this men''s intimate hygiene spray is your everyday essential for modern men’s personal care and all-day comfort.', 'Stay fresh, confident, and irritation-free all day with MENHOOD The Baller Intimate Hygiene Spray for Men—a premium men''s intimate hygiene s…', 4.9, NULL, 'BHD', '["https://f.nooncdn.com/p/pzsku/Z8B7D7244199141780104Z/45/_/1782121541/2cfeef85-e47a-4bf9-9fad-a3654fdf83e7.jpg?width=1200","https://f.nooncdn.com/p/pzsku/Z8B7D7244199141780104Z/45/1755241652/92497f65-04f9-4436-b9b8-caf2faf7c0ff.jpg?width=1200","https://f.nooncdn.com/p/pzsku/Z8B7D7244199141780104Z/45/1755241661/d4c1fe53-3edf-4f5f-a5b8-36415b12e66c.jpg?width=1200","https://f.nooncdn.com/p/pzsku/Z8B7D7244199141780104Z/45/1755241689/c6a4866d-5c4e-4368-b547-9d0888ad0d03.jpg?width=1200"]'::jsonb, (select id from public.categories where slug = 'deodorants-antiperspirants'), (select id from public.brands where slug = 'menhood'), 4.4, 32, 0, true, false, true, ARRAY['personal', 'care', 'deodorants', 'antiperspirants']::text[]),
  ('MENHOOD Intimate Wash for Men 150 ML| Tea Tree Oil Essential Neem Oil | Men Genital Wash |Mens Ball Hygiene |Anti-Fungal Foaming Wash | PH Balanced |Skin Brightening | Long- Lasting Freshness (Green Apple)', 'menhood-intimate-wash-for-men-150-ml-tea-tree-oil-essential-neem-oil-m', 'MENHOOD Intimate Foam Wash for Men is an essential addition to every man’s hygiene routine, offering a clean, refreshing, and irritation-free experience before and after your most intimate moments. Specially formulated as a men''s intimate wash , this premium intimate hygiene wash for men effectively removes dirt, sweat, and bacteria from the men''s private area , while leaving behind a light, refreshing fragrance that keeps you confident all day. Designed for daily use, this advanced intimate wash for men is infused with the natural power of Tea Tree Essential Oil , known for its antibacterial and antifungal properties. It helps soothe itching, reduce irritation, and maintain proper pH balance, making it an ideal men intimate hygiene product for those who work out, groom regularly, or live an active lifestyle. The gentle foaming formula works as a complete men private part wash , providing deep cleansing without dryness or discomfort. Whether you need freshness after the gym, before a date, or as part of your daily shower routine, this intimate foam wash for men ensures long-lasting cleanliness, comfort, and freshness. MENHOOD Intimate Foam Wash is crafted with the same care as facial skincare, because intimate care for men deserves equal attention. More than just hygiene, it supports confidence, comfort, and self-care—making it the perfect men''s hygiene wash for modern men who value cleanliness without compromising masculinity.', 'MENHOOD Intimate Foam Wash for Men is an essential addition to every man’s hygiene routine, offering a clean, refreshing, and irritation-fre…', 2.9, NULL, 'BHD', '["https://f.nooncdn.com/p/pzsku/ZA759D015AF22C3453924Z/45/_/1782022718/9a92ad51-1d09-425c-97