  ('Waterlily Andoil Shower Gel Refreshing Body Wash With Caring Oil Pearls Andfloral Scent Waterlily Andoil 250ml', 'waterlily-andoil-shower-gel-refreshing-body-wash-with-caring-oil-pearl', 'NIVEA Waterlily & Oil Shower Gel provides you with a fresh shower and leaves your skin soft, invigorated and nourished. Enriched with delicious waterlily & care oil pearls, NIVEA Waterlily & Oil Shower Gel envelops your body with a silky, soft foam and stimulates your senses with its refreshing fragrance. It is formulated with Hydra IQ Technology that keeps your skin feeling moisturized even after towel drying. NIVEA Waterlily & Oil Shower Gel is pH skin balanced, dermatologically approved and suitable for all skin types. NIVEA cares for your skin & planet, that''s why this shower gel is microplastic-free, has 98% biodegradable formula (as per OECD or equivalent methods) and its bottle is made in 96% from recycled plastic (excluding cap). At NIVEA we’ve got a vast selection of soaps, shower gels, bath additives, deodorants, creams, lotions, milks and a lot more. If you’re looking for products to help improve the healthy look or glow of your skin, we’ve got you covered! Take a look now and discover the ideal NIVEA product for your needs and preferences. We have products for both men and women including shaving items and deodorants for all of your personal hygiene requirements. NIVEA, a hundred years of skincare for life!', 'NIVEA Waterlily & Oil Shower Gel provides you with a fresh shower and leaves your skin soft, invigorated and nourished.', 1.219, NULL, 'BHD', '["https://f.nooncdn.com/p/pnsku/N11292792A/45/_/1767607992/4536f742-1adc-4fe9-a600-e2d51971a4c8.jpg?width=1200","https://f.nooncdn.com/p/pnsku/N11292792A/45/_/1764236148/7c0bc1ce-3c91-49c9-a53e-7414064a836a.jpg?width=1200","https://f.nooncdn.com/p/pnsku/N11292792A/45/_/1764236151/0c1faf50-5b69-493a-9cdc-b0894fa76d25.jpg?width=1200","https://f.nooncdn.com/p/pnsku/N11292792A/45/_/1764236149/633e4073-1e8b-4184-a0cb-0dc691