  ('Body Lotion Rich Nourishing 72h Moisture Blue 625ml', 'body-lotion-rich-nourishing-72h-moisture-blue-625ml', 'NIVEA Nourishing Body Lotion is a rich, luxurious lotion that is ideal for extra dry and sensitive skin types that have lost their natural moisture. Enriched with skin softening essential almond oil and infused with deep moisture serum, NIVEA Nourishing Body Lotion intensively nourishes your skin for 72hours to noticeably reduce the dryness of your skin just after one application, leaving it soft, smooth and well moisturized. At NIVEA we’ve got a vast selection of soaps, shower gels, bath additives, deodorants, creams, lotions, milks and a lot more. If you’re looking for products to help improve the healthy look or glow of your skin, we’ve got you covered! Take a look now and discover the ideal NIVEA product for your needs and preferences. We have products for both men and women including shaving items and deodorants for all of your personal hygiene requirements. NIVEA, a hundred years of skincare for life!', 'NIVEA Nourishing Body Lotion is a rich, luxurious lotion that is ideal for extra dry and sensitive skin types that have lost their natural m…', 1.961, NULL, 'BHD', '["https://f.nooncdn.com/p/pnsku/N13345734A/45/_/1765870628/eec74c1c-e44e-46b5-aa43-d9d386523f38.jpg?width=1200","https://f.nooncdn.com/p/pnsku/N13345734A/45/_/1764242140/7ad547ba-9e33-44d8-bad5-ceb8d02749e3.jpg?width=1200","https://f.nooncdn.com/p/pnsku/N13345734A/45/_/1764242142/2f8c9dce-9cd4-4ec0-806f-8224886870e2.jpg?width=1200","https://f.nooncdn.com/p/pnsku/N13345734A/45/_/1764242139/8aa335a3-b12e-4313-a55b-50cb370cfcb3.jpg?width=1200"]'::jsonb, (select id from public.categories where slug = 'bath-body'), (select id from public.brands where slug = 'nivea'), 4.5, 642, 0, true, false, true, ARRAY['personal', 'care', 'bath', 'body', 'lotions', 'creams']::text[]),
  ('48 Hours Anti Perspirant Deodorant For Sensitive Skin White 50ml', '48-hours-anti-perspirant-deodorant-for-sensitive-skin-white-50ml', 'Vichy 48 Hours Anti Perspirant Deodorant for Sensitive or depleted skin has a gentle formula, Target perspiration without irritating the skin. Formulated for sensitive skin or post wax or shaving. The anti-perspirant active ingredients combined with soothing Proline Cutei give the skin 48-hour anti-perspiration efficacy and incredible tolerance. Paraben-free, Alcohol-free, Fragrance-free, Hypoallergenic formula. Clinically and dermatologically tested', 'Vichy 48 Hours Anti Perspirant Deodorant for Sensitive or depleted skin has a gentle formula, Target perspiration without irritating the ski…', 4.9, NULL, 'BHD', '["https://f.nooncdn.com/p/pzsku/Z0F553BC507902C641367Z/45/_/1779345222/0997ab04-703f-4f37-87a6-0cba642d2550.jpg?width=1200","https://f.nooncdn.com/p/pzsku/Z0F553BC507902C641367Z/45/_/1779345222/2c937e4e-8e8e-4c8e-af45-dd1047e00874.jpg?width=1200","https://f.nooncdn.com/p/pzsku/Z0F553BC507902C641367Z/45/_/1779345223/4ae8d312-c19b-4750-be65-193329000040.jpg?width=1200","https://f.nooncdn.com/p/pzsku/Z0F553BC507902C641367Z/45/_/1779345223/2528f65c-8f97-43d8-a64a-cbe142ddcc53.jpg?width=1200"]'::jsonb, (select id from public.categories where slug = 'deodorants-antiperspirants'), (select id from public.brands where slug = 'vichy'), 4.4, 293, 0, true, false, true, ARRAY['personal', 'care', 'deodorants', 'antiperspirants']::text[]),
  ('Dry and Bath Body Brush, Reduce Cellulite, Dry Brush for Cellulite and Lymphatic Drainage, Exfoliating Brush with Soft Massage Nodules, Shower Brush Body Scrubber', 'dry-and-bath-body-brush-reduce-cellulite-dry-brush-for-cellulite-and-l', 'Feature: When there are tiny little bumps on your legs or arms, use this exfoliating brush daily, with body wash in the shower. It can also work like a rejuvenating massage to promote blood circulation and the lymphatic system in your body. The pressure of the rubber nodes is like a massage, and the natural bristles of the skin brush are not too hard or too soft. Softening, Massage, Smoothing, Shine, Softness, Pores, Radiant, Clean, Exfoliating, Relaxing, Gentle, Dirt The dry brushing body brush can do exfoliating to help remove dead skin if you have ingrown hairs. body exfoliator can work great to slough off dead skin so ingrown hairs don’t develop, and soften your skin and it would become glowing again without flaky skin. Must Point out that it is slightly painful when cleansing and exfoliating because your dead skin cells are scraped away. If you have a lot of cellulite on your thighs, a Cellulite brush would be your best friend. Simply brush your whole body daily before or after showering in a circling motion from your feet up and when you brush your body completely through with your body scrub brush, you will feel lighter.', 'Feature: When there are tiny little bumps on your legs or arms, use this exfoliating brush daily, with body wash in the shower.', 3.699, NULL, 'BHD', '["https://f.nooncdn.com/p/pzsku/Z2AB5F03FF03E708048FFZ/45/1746292513/09a79fac-7746-4061-a129-0fdd437ed6b6.jpg?width=1200","https://f.nooncdn.com/p/pzsku/Z2AB5F03FF03E708048FFZ/45/1746292513/5657e686-5446-4ef2-9a43-9eb694e6032e.jpg?width=1200","https://f.nooncdn.com/p/pzsku/Z2AB5F03FF03E708048FFZ/45/1746292513/240928f4-7aff-4d47-86c6-04f02fd55713.jpg?width=1200","https://f.nooncdn.com/p/pzsku/Z2AB5F03FF03E708048FFZ/45/1746292514/38dd228b-c87d-4fd3-ad2f-