  ('72 Hours Stress Resist Excessive Perspiration Deodorant White/Red 50ml', '72-hours-stress-resist-excessive-perspiration-deodorant-white-red-50ml', 'Vichy 72 Hours Stress Resist Excessive Perspiration Deodorant is a Hyper-effective anti-perspirant, for up to 72 hour protection even under stressful situations. Rich in anti-perspirant active ingredients, ultra-absorbent minerals and Perspicalm, this anti-perspirant regulates heat and perspiration at times of stress. Protected, you feel secure all day long. Formula tested on sensitive skin, alochol-free and paraben-free', 'Vichy 72 Hours Stress Resist Excessive Perspiration Deodorant is a Hyper-effective anti-perspirant, for up to 72 hour protection even under…', 4.994, NULL, 'BHD', '["https://f.nooncdn.com/p/pzsku/ZF17B6E8BC8010E2D486FZ/45/_/1779344999/6e9c8649-6744-44ae-b279-d65d5ce76624.jpg?width=1200","https://f.nooncdn.com/p/pzsku/ZF17B6E8BC8010E2D486FZ/45/_/1779344999/bc6261c8-1eb5-48d1-a92c-a2af831d28ed.jpg?width=1200","https://f.nooncdn.com/p/pzsku/ZF17B6E8BC8010E2D486FZ/45/_/1779344999/103e5acf-3a05-4047-915f-936d2bb99a2c.jpg?width=1200","https://f.nooncdn.com/p/pzsku/ZF17B6E8BC8010E2D486FZ/45/_/1779344999/f2b9153a-a983-4c9b-98b1-e95e7a457a2f.jpg?width=1200"]'::jsonb, (select id from public.categories where slug = 'deodorants-antiperspirants'), (select id from public.brands where slug = 'vichy'), 4.4, 199, 0, true, false, true, ARRAY['personal', 'care', 'deodorants', 'antiperspirants']::text[]),
