  ('Lip Oil Golden Shimmer - Honey infused', 'lip-oil-golden-shimmer-honey-infused', 'Intense Hydration: Infused with Mirsalehi Honey and Hyaluronic Acid, provides deep hydration to keep lips soft and supple.. Smoothing Effect: Mirsalehi Bee Garden Oil Blend instantly smooths lips, reducing fine lines and dryness.. Plumping Action: Natural actives plump lips, giving them a fuller and more defined appearance.. Enhanced Natural Color: Mirsalehi Honey highlights and enhances the lips'' natural color, leaving a healthy shine.. Versatile Use: Can be used alone as a nourishing lip treatment, under or over lip color for added hydration and shine.. Mirsalehi Honey: Known for its hydrating and nourishing properties, provides essential moisture to lips.', 'Intense Hydration: Infused with Mirsalehi Honey and Hyaluronic Acid, provides deep hydration to keep lips soft and supple..', 3.372, NULL, 'BHD', '["https://f.nooncdn.com/p/pzsku/ZA219E5B6EACAD67891DEZ/45/1745228996/e4249be8-4ac9-462f-90fd-1a53fc3ac2ed.jpg?width=1200","https://f.nooncdn.com/p/pzsku/ZA219E5B6EACAD67891DEZ/45/1745228997/0deebe00-b01b-4029-ba33-7b9172b65454.jpg?width=1200","https://f.nooncdn.com/p/pzsku/ZA219E5B6EACAD67891DEZ/45/1745228997/f3fecbd8-7a0e-4fe7-aa0c-ade41ad31702.jpg?width=1200","https://f.nooncdn.com/p/pzsku/ZA219E5B6EACAD67891DEZ/45/1745228997/aa8e1ce8-d8b3-4452-8dbd-2ff177a1755e.jpg?width=1200"]'::jsonb, (select id from public.categories where slug = 'lips'), (select id from public.brands where slug = 'gisou'), 4.1, 22, 0, true, false, true, ARRAY['makeup', 'lips', 'lip', 'glosses']::text[]),
  ('Fat Oil Lip Drip, Moisturizing, Shiny, Vegan Tinted Lip Gloss, Non-Sticky, 12H Hydration, Squalane, Raspberry & Cloudberry Oils -', 'fat-oil-lip-drip-moisturizing-shiny-vegan-tinted-lip-gloss-non-sticky-zc99d9', 'Say hello to Fat Oil, our first lip drip of its kind. Lips drippin'' with FAT perks. FAT SHINE. FAT CARE. FAT 12 HR HYDRATION. The fat family is getting FATTER! Wear it alone or layer it over lip liner or lipstick for added color and shine. Get ready for 6 new CREAMY shades. Fat Oil has a high shine finish with comfortable wear and a non-sticky texture. Packed with FAT goodness to keep your lips dripping using cloudberry oil, raspberry oil and squalane. The best part? You are one swipe away from FAT perks. Vegan. Cruelty-free.', 'Say hello to Fat Oil, our first lip drip of its kind. Lips drippin'' with FAT perks. FAT SHINE. FAT CARE. FAT 12 HR HYDRATION.', 5.645, NULL, 'BHD', '["https://f.nooncdn.com/p/pzsku/ZC99D9F1E28A768D227BFZ/45/_/1739784032/d0745e00-bb10-4d64-a290-b1cd5384eb26.jpg?width=1200","https://f.nooncdn.com/p/pzsku/ZC99D9F1E28A768D227BFZ/45/_/1739784151/05529104-21dd-493b-a9e7-fd12d6b13e19.jpg?width=1200","https://f.nooncdn.com/p/pzsku/ZC99D9F1E28A768D227BFZ/45/_/1739784034/7b879ab6-47a0-493f-8cfc-7b76f78b9856.jpg?width=1200","https://f.nooncdn.com/p/pzsku/ZC99D9F1E28A768D227BFZ/45/_/1739784035/6e508df9-2623-48c3-ade3-c8983e0c6133.jpg?width=1200"]'::jsonb, (select id from public.categories where slug = 'lips'), (select id from public.brands where slug = 'nyx-professional-makeup'), 4.6, 4915, 0, true, false, true, ARRAY['makeup', 'lips', 'lip', 'glosses']::text[]),
