  ('Bomb Hit Lip Gloss And Plumper Glow Heat', 'bomb-hit-lip-gloss-and-plumper-glow-heat', 'Fenty Beauty lip gloss is a non-sticky lip gloss with a moisturizing shine. Crystal light high shine liquid lip gloss gives you soft and hydrated lips. This liquid lip gloss contains a combination of bright and vibrant lipsticks. Its formula contains ginger root oil and pepper fruit extract, to give the lips a pleasant finish and plump. It also contains moisturizing shea butter and vitamin E to keep your lips hydrated', 'Fenty Beauty lip gloss is a non-sticky lip gloss with a moisturizing shine.', 2.105, NULL, 'BHD', '["https://f.nooncdn.com/p/pzsku/ZB50E858A2CF9B26E4BCCZ/45/_/1779873378/5a6087bb-f973-47fe-9d72-792b74476743.jpg?width=1200","https://f.nooncdn.com/p/pzsku/ZB50E858A2CF9B26E4BCCZ/45/_/1779873378/0dccb366-df4a-41b9-894b-58e616272f88.jpg?width=1200","https://f.nooncdn.com/p/pzsku/ZB50E858A2CF9B26E4BCCZ/45/_/1779873378/7bde9db2-b210-4628-b033-7a9a11f45e30.jpg?width=1200","https://f.nooncdn.com/p/pzsku/ZB50E858A2CF9B26E4BCCZ/45/_/1779873379/573e59c8-7d72-41af-9fdb-41153f49a27b.jpg?width=1200"]'::jsonb, (select id from public.categories where slug = 'lips'), (select id from public.brands where slug = 'fenty-beauty'), 3.6, 465, 0, true, false, true, ARRAY['makeup', 'lips', 'lip', 'glosses']::text[]),
  ('Moisturizing Cream For Dry Skin With Hyaluronic Acid - 340grams', 'moisturizing-cream-for-dry-skin-with-hyaluronic-acid-340grams', 'CeraVe Moisturizing Cream includes three essential ceramides and hyaluronic acid to effectively hydrate the skin and restore the skin’s protective barrier. Developed with dermatologists and suitable for dry and very dry skin on the face and body, this rich, non-greasy, fast-absorbing moisturizing cream features our patented MVE Delivery Technology to release a steady stream of moisturizing ingredients throughout the day and night. While a compromised skin barrier can lead to dryness and itching, a moisturizing cream with hyaluronic acid and ceramides can help. By hydrating the skin and restoring its natural barrier, a cream with these ingredients can help those with even dry to very dry skin improve the look and feel of their skin. CeraVe Moisturizing Cream with ceramides is fragrance free. Usage for Men and Women. Safe for babies 2 months and older.', 'CeraVe Moisturizing Cream includes three essential ceramides and hyaluronic acid to effectively hydrate the skin and restore the skin’s prot…', 6.795, NULL, 'BHD', '["https://f.nooncdn.com/p/pzsku/ZB7A0F7CD9D36851D2A87Z/45/_/1779179138/457bd44f-3865-4b9e-883e-65988bf71af9.jpg?width=1200","https://f.nooncdn.com/p/pzsku/ZB7A0F7CD9D36851D2A87Z/45/_/1779179138/f2137f4d-b679-46a7-b638-865e988b77e0.jpg?width=1200","https://f.nooncdn.com/p/pzsku/ZB7A0F7CD9D36851D2A87Z/45/_/1779179138/512e3bfe-50f4-47bb-b25d-f9b1336ce8e1.jpg?width=1200","https://f.nooncdn.com/p/pzsku/ZB7A0F7CD9D36851D2A87Z/45/_/1779179139/c254b3e0-b4ab-4e95-92f0-e547d02125c8.jpg?width=1200"]'::jsonb, (select id from public.categories where slug = 'creams-moisturizers'), (select id from public.brands where slug = 'cerave'), 4.4, 5875, 0, true, false, true, ARRAY['skin', 'care', 'creams', 'moisturizers', 'face']::text[]),
  ('Moisturising Lotion For Normal To Dry Skin With 3 Essential Ceramides white 236ml', 'moisturising-lotion-for-normal-to-dry-skin-with-3-essential-ceramides', 'CeraVe Daily Moisturizing Lotion is a lightweight, oil-free moisturizer that helps hydrate the skin and restore its natural barrier. Formulated with three essential ceramides and hyaluronic acid, it also features patented MVE Technology for long-lasting hydration and a lightweight, non-comedogenic formula that won’t clog pores. Our daily moisturizer leaves the skin feeling comfortable and is gentle on the skin as it provides 24-hour hydration. Usage for Men and Women. Safe for babies 2 months and older.', 'CeraVe Daily Moisturizing Lotion is a lightweight, oil-free moisturizer that helps hydrate the skin and restore its natural barrier.', 5.595, NULL, 'BHD', '["https://f.nooncdn.com/p/pzsku/Z0381910905748174F0DCZ/45/_/1779179010/67bb178e-023d-492f-9cc0-1101273ca810.jpg?width=1200","https://f.nooncdn.com/p/pzsku/Z0381910905748174F0DCZ/45/_/1779179010/8f3b0866-8004-41e9-bc6e-7c984c066277.jpg?width=1200","https://f.nooncdn.com/p/pzsku/Z0381910905748174F0DCZ/45/_/1779179010/54a8fefd-c50f-41f7-ac9b-1e0e685e135f.jpg?width=1200","https://f.nooncdn.com/p/pzsku/Z0381910905748174F0DCZ/45/_/1779179010/4991e688-9bbb-423e-80d8-89a453a921db.jpg?width=1200"]'::jsonb, (select id from public.categories where slug = 'creams-moisturizers'), (select id from public.brands where slug = 'cerave'), 4.5, 7213, 0, true, false, true, ARRAY['skin', 'care', 'creams', 'moisturizers', 'face']::text[]),
  ('Moisturizing Lotion For Dry To Very Dry Skin With Hyaluronic Acid 473ml', 'moisturizing-lotion-for-dry-to-very-dry-skin-with-hyaluronic-acid-473m', 'CeraVe Daily Moisturizing Lotion is a lightweight, oil-free moisturizer that helps hydrate the skin and restore its natural barrier. Formulated with three essential ceramides and hyaluronic acid, it also features patented MVE Technology for long-lasting hydration and a lightweight, non-comedogenic formula that won’t clog pores. Our daily moisturizer leaves the skin feeling comfortable and is gentle on the skin as it provides 24-hour hydration.', 'CeraVe Daily Moisturizing Lotion is a lightweight, oil-free moisturizer that helps hydrate the skin and restore its natural barrier.', 8.695, NULL, 'BHD', '["https://f.nooncdn.com/p/pzsku/ZA726B0AA5E20B2E00DCCZ/45/_/1779179263/2840689a-f680-4bfc-9460-d57f5d51ec2b.jpg?width=1200","https://f.nooncdn.com/p/pzsku/ZA726B0AA5E20B2E00DCCZ/45/_/1779179263/a45b7d09-4e48-4262-a93e-dd34c6c7733b.jpg?width=1200","https://f.nooncdn.com/p/pzsku/ZA726B0AA5E20B2E00DCCZ/45/_/1779179263/51da70fb-46ae-460b-8f0f-479ea4b099cb.jpg?width=1200","https://f.nooncdn.com/p/pzsku/ZA726B0AA5E20B2E00DCCZ/45/_/1779179263/2a4b6d35-75c9-4bb4-84d3-cc40c0572ba9.jpg?width=1200"]'::jsonb, (select id from public.categories where slug = 'creams-moisturizers'), (select id from public.brands where slug = 'cerave'), 4.5, 7213, 0, true, false, true, ARRAY['skin', 'care', 'creams', 'moisturizers', 'face']::text[]),
  ('Intensive Moisturising Lotion For Very Dry, Itchy Skin 236ml', 'intensive-moisturising-lotion-for-very-dry-itchy-skin-236ml', 'CeraVe Intensive Moisturising Lotion is designed to relieve and protect against five key signs of dryness—itchiness, tightness, rough texture, flakiness, and redness or discoloration caused by dryness. This fast-absorbing body moisturiser for dry skin penetrates the skin’s surface to provide intense hydration without leaving a greasy or sticky residue. Formulated with three essential ceramides, the lotion also strengthens the skin barrier. CeraVe Intensive Moisturising Lotion also includes hyaluronic acid and 5% Hydro-Urea (composed of natural moisturising factors). Featuring MVE Delivery Technology, this formula continuously releases moisturising ingredients for up to 72 hours of hydration. It’s allergy-tested, fragrance-free, pH-balanced, and suitable for all skin types, including sensitive skin. Usage for men and women.', 'CeraVe Intensive Moisturising Lotion is designed to relieve and protect against five key signs of dryness—itchiness, tightness, rough textur…', 13.2, NULL, 'BHD', '["https://f.nooncdn.com/p/pzsku/ZB3FF90FE785C27E332A8Z/45/_/1783338065/94efc222-379f-47a9-9474-0ffdcfa32dbf.jpg?width=1200","https://f.nooncdn.com/p/pzsku/ZB3FF90FE785C27E332A8Z/45/_/1783338065/9de57330-a02e-475e-aa91-7c656e1041db.jpg?width=1200","https://f.nooncdn.com/p/pzsku/ZB3FF90FE785C27E332A8Z/45/_/1783338065/cb1d00dd-95ea-4627-bc27-7da3f8029969.jpg?width=1200","https://f.nooncdn.com/p/pzsku/ZB3FF90FE785C27E332A8Z/45/_/1783338065/28d384c5-d2ab-4834-8108-0144c2da8677.jpg?width=1200"]'::jsonb, (select id from public.categories where slug = 'creams-moisturizers'), (select id from public.brands where slug = 'cerave'), 4.6, 150, 0, true, false, true, ARRAY['skin', 'care', 'creams', 'moisturizers', 'face']::text[]),
  ('Am Facial Moisturizing Lotion Spf50 For Normal To Dry Skin 52ml', 'am-facial-moisturizing-lotion-spf50-for-normal-to-dry-skin-52ml', 'Developed with dermatologists, CeraVe AM Facial Moisturising Lotion combines moisturiser and sunscreen to hydrate your skin while helping to absorb and reflect the sun’s damaging rays. This daytime multitasker features broad-spectrum SPF 50 sunscreen and beneficial ingredients like our three essential ceramides, hyaluronic acid, and niacinamide. It also includes MVE Delivery Technology, which releases a steady stream of moisturizing ingredients for continuous, all-day hydration.', 'Developed with dermatologists, CeraVe AM Facial Moisturising Lotion combines moisturiser and sunscreen to hydrate your skin while helping to…', 11.9, NULL, 'BHD', '["https://f.nooncdn.com/p/pzsku/Z1F76CA7AD773C725CE83Z/45/_/1778231350/2f1d84e1-37e0-4544-a92b-6c76335f17d9.jpg?width=1200","https://f.nooncdn.com/p/pzsku/Z1F76CA7AD773C725CE83Z/45/_/1778231348/51e854e3-9dc6-4841-97b1-344b9bacd74d.jpg?width=1200","https://f.nooncdn.com/p/pzsku/Z1F76CA7AD773C725CE83Z/45/_/1778231347/7c3a4e6f-3a6d-48f7-b27e-5484e4bb9c7a.jpg?width=1200","https://f.nooncdn.com/p/pzsku/Z1F76CA7AD773C725CE83Z/45/_/1778231348/5ff4bf05-25ee-4404-a865-7b20cb9cd31a.jpg?width=1200"]'::jsonb, (select id from public.categories where slug = 'creams-moisturizers'), (select id from public.brands where slug = 'cerave'), 4.6, 802, 0, true, false, true, ARRAY['skin', 'care', 'creams', 'moisturizers', 'face']::text[]),
  ('Moisturizing Cream, Dry to Very Dry, Sensitive Skin, Hydrates for 48 hours, Restores skin barrier, Face And Body For Men And Women, Non-Comedogenic ,With Niacinamide And Vitamin B5, Unscented 453grams', 'moisturizing-cream-dry-to-very-dry-sensitive-skin-hydrates-for-48-hour', 'Skin type: Dry to Very Dry Skin Rich cream is clinically proven to hydrate for 48 hours and fully restores skin''s moisture barrier. • Specially formulated with a dermatologist-backed blend of niacinamide (vitamin B3), panthenol (vitamin B5) and hydrating glycerin to improve the resilience of sensitive skin . • Significant skin barrier improvement in 3 days with complete restoration in 1 week . • 97% of users reported that skin seems more hydrated over time . • Dermatologist tested and clinically proven to be gentle on sensitive skin. • Accepted by the National Eczema Association to be gentle on eczema-prone skin.', 'Skin type: Dry to Very Dry Skin Rich cream is clinically proven to hydrate for 48 hours and fully restores skin''s moisture barrier.', 6.014, NULL, 'BHD', '["https://f.nooncdn.com/p/pzsku/ZAEECA13950690967F81AZ/45/_/1778592169/242b712f-c3f4-4a13-8689-1e2ab8292e7d.jpg?width=1200","https://f.nooncdn.com/p/pzsku/ZAEECA13950690967F81AZ/45/_/1778592169/28c98084-1b22-4514-a619-3c3feb245086.jpg?width=1200","https://f.nooncdn.com/p/pzsku/ZAEECA13950690967F81AZ/45/_/1778592169/1982680d-dd9d-4032-853b-6c4752326c87.jpg?width=1200","https://f.nooncdn.com/p/pzsku/ZAEECA13950690967F81AZ/45/_/1778592169/1e45464f-e020-4782-8632-b316fc2b42a1.jpg?width=1200"]'::jsonb, (select id from public.categories where slug = 'creams-moisturizers'), (select id from public.brands where slug = 'cetaphil'), 0, 0, 0, true, false, true, ARRAY['skin', 'care', 'creams', 'moisturizers', 'face']::text[]),
  ('Moisturizing Cream White 500grams', 'moisturizing-cream-white-500grams', 'Recommended for moisturising dry skin Helps to seal in natural moisture by acting as a protective barrier Suitable for skin conditions such as dry, scaly skin, eczema, psoriasis and dermatitis PH balanced, low-irritant formulation, free from fragran', 'Recommended for moisturising dry skin Helps to seal in natural moisture by acting as a protective barrier Suitable for skin conditions such…', 4.2, NULL, 'BHD', '["https://f.nooncdn.com/p/pzsku/Z28773FE336DCD2B229F6Z/45/_/1778592465/212ad4c7-83a5-4bd6-8553-7f4324bc2c24.jpg?width=1200","https://f.nooncdn.com/p/pzsku/Z28773FE336DCD2B229F6Z/45/_/1778592465/1b44103f-e141-4653-9b20-113ce7a913a6.jpg?width=1200","https://f.nooncdn.com/p/pzsku/Z28773FE336DCD2B229F6Z/45/_/1778592465/0b5ccf89-e79d-41ee-b03d-133586a6be6d.jpg?width=1200","https://f.nooncdn.com/p/pzsku/Z28773FE336DCD2B229F6Z/45/_/1778592465/27b06c79-6a24-44b9-85d3-adb0cf121fe2.jpg?width=1200"]'::jsonb, (select id from public.categories where slug = 'creams-moisturizers'), (select id from public.brands where slug = 'qv'), 3.1, 379, 0, true, false, true, ARRAY['skin', 'care', 'creams', 'moisturizers', 'face']::text[]),
  ('Moisturizing Cream Very Dry To Dry Sensitive Skin 566grams', 'moisturizing-cream-very-dry-to-dry-sensitive-skin-566grams', 'Instantly replenishes, intensely nourishes and soothes skin dryness for 48 hours.. Binds water to the skin, preventing moisture loss to hydrate and protect skin from dryness.. Now with hydrating glycerin and skin essential vitamins B5 (panthenol) and B3 (niacinamide).. Hypoallergenic formula is also noncomedogenic so it wont clog pores or irritate sensitive skin.. All CETAPHIL products are effective yet non-irritating.', 'Instantly replenishes, intensely nourishes and soothes skin dryness for 48 hours..', 4.465, NULL, 'BHD', '["https://f.nooncdn.com/p/pzsku/ZFEEEC381512C60654597Z/45/_/1778592201/06f4e8a1-4eff-4cfb-ad3b-6612db7432ce.jpg?width=1200","https://f.nooncdn.com/p/pzsku/ZFEEEC381512C60654597Z/45/_/1778592201/c86a30dd-2c6d-49c0-8266-a450306eafe1.jpg?width=1200","https://f.nooncdn.com/p/pzsku/ZFEEEC381512C60654597Z/45/_/1778592201/155f0c02-0da2-46a1-a2f0-a3dfd5bf4235.jpg?width=1200","https://f.nooncdn.com/p/pzsku/ZFEEEC381512C60654597Z/45/_/1778592201/8accd60c-5d86-4493-a846-12cef6f88385.jpg?width=1200"]'::jsonb, (select id from public.categories where slug = 'creams-moisturizers'), (select id from public.brands where slug = 'cetaphil'), 4.5, 1348, 0, true, false, true, ARRAY['skin', 'care', 'creams', 'moisturizers', 'face']::text[]),
  ('HYA ACID SERUM 50 MIL', 'hya-acid-serum-50-mil', 'Product Description : Seb Beauty HYA ACID Serum is a product designed to hydrate and improve the appearance of the skin. It contains a formula rich in hyaluronic acid, a powerful humectant that helps attract and retain moisture in the skin, making it look fuller and more radiant. The serum also contains Centella Asiatica extract, a natural ingredient that helps soothe the skin and reduce inflammation, as well as stimulate collagen production, which improves skin elasticity and reduces the appearance of wrinkles. The serum helps tighten the skin and improve its texture, making it look younger and brighter. The serum comes in an easy-to-use dropper bottle, allowing for an appropriate amount of product to be applied to the skin. How to use : After cleansing and drying your skin, apply a few drops of serum to your face and neck. Gently massage the serum into the skin until completely absorbed. Use the serum morning and evening for best results. A moisturizer can be used after the serum if needed.', 'Product Description : Seb Beauty HYA ACID Serum is a product designed to hydrate and improve the appearance of the skin.', 2.42, NULL, 'BHD', '["https://f.nooncdn.com/p/pzsku/Z766784844535558EC704Z/45/1741436785/c8f467c5-0184-486b-9224-259f57111ceb.jpg?width=1200","https://f.nooncdn.com/p/pzsku/Z766784844535558EC704Z/45/1741436790/65e2002e-432e-4cea-8652-f167d320665c.jpg?width=1200","https://f.nooncdn.com/p/pzsku/Z766784844535558EC704Z/45/1741436800/e3154587-280f-465a-8143-8a27c5c4ca54.jpg?width=1200","https://f.nooncdn.com/p/pzsku/Z766784844535558EC704Z/45/1741436805/aabb780d-8df4-4193-91c9-fe5da83da44c.jpg?width=1200"]'::jsonb, (select id from public.categories where slug = 'treatment-serums'), (select id from public.brands where slug = 'sipbeauty'), 4, 3, 0, true, false, true, ARRAY['skin', 'care', 'treatment', 'serums', 'face']::text[]),
  ('vitamin C serum', 'vitamin-c-serum', 'Product Description : Seb Beauty Vitamin C Serum is a product designed to moisturize and brighten the skin, improving its overall appearance. Contains a high concentration of Vitamin C (20%), a powerful antioxidant that helps protect skin from free radical damage, lighten dark spots, and stimulate collagen production, leaving skin looking younger and brighter. The serum formula is designed to provide deep hydration to dry skin, leaving it soft and supple. The serum features an advanced skincare formula, making it effective in improving the appearance of the skin and fighting signs of aging. The serum comes in an easy-to-use dropper bottle, allowing for an appropriate amount of product to be applied to the skin How to use : After cleansing and drying your skin, apply a few drops of serum to your face and neck. Gently massage the serum into the skin until completely absorbed. Use the serum morning and evening for best results.', 'Product Description : Seb Beauty Vitamin C Serum is a product designed to moisturize and brighten the skin, improving its overall appearance…', 2.5, NULL, 'BHD', '["https://f.nooncdn.com/p/pzsku/Z88CA6D9408A001427894Z/45/_/1778148882/394f425b-e0db-4724-ab1a-0a1d806b9586.jpg?width=1200","https://f.nooncdn.com/p/pzsku/Z88CA6D9408A001427894Z/45/_/1778148887/6cbd1ab9-1d7b-407d-9c7c-c13e70a9ae3b.jpg?width=1200","https://f.nooncdn.com/p/pzsku/Z88CA6D9408A001427894Z/45/_/1778148882/6eee9559-63ab-4c9e-a4fc-b5ee2e5c1248.jpg?width=1200","https://f.nooncdn.com/p/pzsku/Z88CA6D9408A001427894Z/45/_/1778148882/7c354741-23fd-410a-b609-73295e6a1b9f.jpg?width=1200"]'::jsonb, (select id from public.categories where slug = 'treatment-serums'), (select id from public.brands where slug = 'sipbeauty'), 4.4, 16, 0, true, false, true, ARRAY['skin', 'care', 'treatment', 'serums', 'face']::text[]),
  ('Even Pigment Perfector Skin Perfecting Face Serum with Thiamidol and Hyaluronic Acid 30 Ml', 'even-pigment-perfector-skin-perfecting-face-serum-with-thiamidol-and-h', 'The sun, hormonal influences and aging can trigger hyperpigmentation, leading to dark patches and age spots. Even Pigment Perfector range has been specially formulated with our patented ingredient, Thiamidol, to effectively reduce hyperpigmentation for more even and radiant skin. Eucerin Even Pigment Perfecting Face Serum is developed to help reduce pigment spots and promote skin’s natural radiance. Thiamidol acts at the root cause of hyperpigmentation by reducing melanin production. It is not only proven to reduce dark spots but also prevent their reappearance. The face serum’s potent formula is further enriched with Hyaluronic Acid, an active ingredient that provides and retains moisture levels for more rejuvenated, smooth and supple skin. With regular use, see visible results after two weeks and witness further improvement in the skin over time. This face serum for pigmentation is clinically and dermatologically proven to show good skin tolerability and reduce pigment spots and prevent their reappearance. It is proven to make skill more radiant naturally.', 'The sun, hormonal influences and aging can trigger hyperpigmentation, leading to dark patches and age spots.', 17.932, NULL, 'BHD', '["https://f.nooncdn.com/p/pzsku/Z52EE8EF792F9DABE0590Z/45/1761202599/40f0f4e3-fcb2-462d-b298-93391ebaceef.jpg?width=1200","https://f.nooncdn.com/p/pzsku/Z52EE8EF792F9DABE0590Z/45/1762868065/8a4a9bb3-709e-41a2-afdb-5f2ee22f599a.jpg?width=1200","https://f.nooncdn.com/p/pzsku/Z52EE8EF792F9DABE0590Z/45/1762868066/41d6f9b7-30cd-49ff-b088-8f22daaf8324.jpg?width=1200","https://f.nooncdn.com/p/pzsku/Z52EE8EF792F9DABE0590Z/45/1762868066/5065e5bd-5610-448b-b660-ac919f7335ff.jpg?width=1200"]'::jsonb, (select id from public.categories where slug = 'treatment-serums'), (select id from public.brands where slug = 'eucerin'), 0, 0, 0, true, false, true, ARRAY['skin', 'care', 'treatment', 'serums', 'face']::text[]),
  ('Arencia Vitamin C Booster Shot Serum with Glutathione, Niacinamide and Vitamin E for Dark Spot Care, Fine Lines & Wrinkles, Glass Skin, Korean Skincare 30ml/1.01 fl.oz', 'arencia-vitamin-c-booster-shot-serum-with-glutathione-niacinamide-and', 'Powered by Vitamin C to visibly brighten dull skin, fade dark spots, and even skin tone, revealing a clear, radiant Korean glass skin effect.. Infused with Glutathione and Niacinamide to target pigmentation, acne marks, sun spots, and discoloration for a smoother, more even complexion.. Enriched with Vitamin E and antioxidants to reduce the appearance of fine lines, wrinkles, and early signs of aging while improving skin elasticity.. Lightweight yet deeply hydrating formula helps strengthen the skin barrier, lock in moisture, and keep skin soft, plump, and healthy-looking all day.. Non-sticky, fast-absorbing serum suitable for all skin types, including sensitive skin. Perfect for daily use and layering with other skincare products.', 'Powered by Vitamin C to visibly brighten dull skin, fade dark spots, and even skin tone, revealing a clear, radiant Korean glass skin effect…', 3.59, NULL, 'BHD', '["https://f.nooncdn.com/p/pzsku/Z781C2C17E6DE104C4D0AZ/45/_/1773730650/591428f8-9da3-4035-8d16-41e0bead938f.jpg?width=1200","https://f.nooncdn.com/p/pzsku/Z781C2C17E6DE104C4D0AZ/45/_/1773730651/d92e3976-ff47-4b11-abe3-0160753d0b29.jpg?width=1200","https://f.nooncdn.com/p/pzsku/Z781C2C17E6DE104C4D0AZ/45/_/1773730651/57908fcf-01c9-46bb-854a-dc3f56b08a34.jpg?width=1200","https://f.nooncdn.com/p/pzsku/Z781C2C17E6DE104C4D0AZ/45/_/1773731571/13809024-be31-43e7-a2b4-51b5143f7b5e.jpg?width=1200"]'::jsonb, (select id from public.categories where slug = 'treatment-serums'), (select id from public.brands where slug = 'arencia'), 4.8, 17, 0, true, false, true, ARRAY['skin', 'care', 'treatment', 'serums', 'face']::text[]),
  ('Dark Spot Clearing Turmeric Serum', 'dark-spot-clearing-turmeric-serum', '• Visibly Reduces Dark Spots in 1 Week. • Visibly diminishes dark spots, sunspots, age spots, and blemishes in 1 Week. • Improves hydration, soothes skin & enhances skin’s natural barrier function. • Reduces dullness & enhances skin radiance. • It is Light and fast absorbing serum. • This non-staining serum is made with organically sourced Turmeric and cold pressed Turmeric Extract. • With 10% Glycolic acid & 2% Niacinamide. • Free from Parabens and Phthalates.', '• Visibly Reduces Dark Spots in 1 Week. • Visibly diminishes dark spots, sunspots, age spots, and blemishes in 1 Week.', 3.295, NULL, 'BHD', '["https://f.nooncdn.com/p/pzsku/Z2EF24845F020A6766BE6Z/45/1755950690/5a0def47-ab4a-458c-bc96-e68708ee5669.jpg?width=1200","https://f.nooncdn.com/p/pzsku/Z2EF24845F020A6766BE6Z/45/1755950689/9ba5ffbd-3ca7-4c00-8bb9-cf16e68e4b73.jpg?width=1200","https://f.nooncdn.com/p/pzsku/Z2EF24845F020A6766BE6Z/45/1755950689/678c911d-20a1-4f80-af5d-f6f94aaa200a.jpg?width=1200","https://f.nooncdn.com/p/pzsku/Z2EF24845F020A6766BE6Z/45/1755950690/fbfa2749-8d08-41b0-a9b9-2a9a3909727a.jpg?width=1200"]'::jsonb, (select id from public.categories where slug = 'treatment-serums'), (select id from public.brands where slug = 'himalaya'), 4, 11, 0, true, false, true, ARRAY['skin', 'care', 'treatment', 'serums', 'masks']::text[]),
  ('Red Bean Refreshing Pore Mask Red 140ml', 'red-bean-refreshing-pore-mask-red-140ml', 'Product description- Our pores are the channels through which sebum exits our skin. Excess sebum and dead skin cells accumulate in these channels, causing the pores to enlarge. For pore care, you need to remove dead skin cells in the pores, wash away the accumulated sebum and waste, and then lower the skin''s temperature. For pore and exfoliation care, which is the beginning of skin care, we found the ingredients from the Earth, home to our beginning. Ingredients- Phaseolus angularis seed extract, glycerin, kaolin, caprylic/capric triglyceride, 1,2-hexanediol, phaseolus angularis seed powder, hectorite, cetyl alcohol, glyceryl stearate se, sorbitan olivate, cetearyl olivate, ultramarines, pyrus communis (pear) fruit extract, ethylhexylglycerin, sodium acrylate/sodium acryloyldimethyl taurate copolymer, hedera helix (ivy) leaf/stem extract, water, polyisobutene, pyrus malus (apple) leaf extract, fragaria chiloensis (strawberry) fruit extract, ci 77491.', 'Product description- Our pores are the channels through which sebum exits our skin.', 4.935, NULL, 'BHD', '["https://f.nooncdn.com/p/pzsku/ZD3256B8384ECC54F636DZ/45/_/1778231233/2ecbe22f-f24e-4d2a-8025-357399ca0ba1.jpg?width=1200","https://f.nooncdn.com/p/pzsku/ZD3256B8384ECC54F636DZ/45/_/1778231233/61af32b9-661b-424c-b174-ed741980371e.jpg?width=1200","https://f.nooncdn.com/p/pzsku/ZD3256B8384ECC54F636DZ/45/_/1778231234/633451eb-a400-4938-8189-99f2680b54f3.jpg?width=1200","https://f.nooncdn.com/p/pzsku/ZD3256B8384ECC54F636DZ/45/_/1778231234/bfb8fa76-f4d8-4a31-b370-e897d2d2dab7.jpg?width=1200"]'::jsonb, (select id from public.categories where slug = 'treatment-serums'), (select id from public.brands where slug = 'beauty-of-joseon'), 4.5, 156, 0, true, false, true, ARRAY['skin', 'care', 'treatment', 'serums', 'masks']::text[]),
  ('Retinal Booster Shot Serum, Face and Eye Serum Moisturizer with Caffeine and Ectoin for Mature Skin, Pore Minimizing, Fine Lines & Wrinkles, Korean Skincare', 'retinal-booster-shot-serum-face-and-eye-serum-moisturizer-with-caffein', 'Retinal-Infused Renewal: Promotes smoother, more refined-looking skin overnight.. Texture Refinement: Helps visibly reduce roughness and uneven surface for a polished, radiant appearance.. Nourishing Lipids: Helps maintain moisture and keep skin feeling comfortable and hydrated.. Peptide-Enriched Formula: Supports a firm, resilient, and healthy-looking complexion.. Comfortable Nighttime Hydration: Lightweight, non-greasy texture absorbs easily without irritation.', 'Retinal-Infused Renewal: Promotes smoother, more refined-looking skin overnight..', 4.6, NULL, 'BHD', '["https://f.nooncdn.com/p/pzsku/Z5778A52AE14463264BFBZ/45/_/1772440825/c6467481-e3dd-4b3f-b8ec-4289537e62b0.jpg?width=1200","https://f.nooncdn.com/p/pzsku/Z5778A52AE14463264BFBZ/45/_/1772440825/68cdd9f8-b1a3-4090-a248-b9976c11cb2b.jpg?width=1200","https://f.nooncdn.com/p/pzsku/Z5778A52AE14463264BFBZ/45/_/1772440825/6eb7bdaf-bb62-4547-8001-bed48bb8d2a4.jpg?width=1200","https://f.nooncdn.com/p/pzsku/Z5778A52AE14463264BFBZ/45/_/1772440825/a22596c2-e738-47f0-b376-641563dff256.jpg?width=1200"]'::jsonb, (select id from public.categories where slug = 'treatment-serums'), (select id from public.brands where slug = 'arencia'), 4.7, 3, 0, true, false, true, ARRAY['skin', 'care', 'treatment', 'serums', 'face']::text[]),
  ('Naturals Vitamin C Face Serum 30 mil', 'naturals-vitamin-c-face-serum-30-mil', 'Vitamin C Facial Serum is a skin care product enriched with Vitamin C, mostly in the form of pure ascorbic acid. It is known for its powerful antioxidant properties, which helps protect the skin from damage caused by free radicals and environmental aggressors.', 'Vitamin C Facial Serum is a skin care product enriched with Vitamin C, mostly in the form of pure ascorbic acid.', 1.62, NULL, 'BHD', '["https://f.nooncdn.com/p/pzsku/Z3CBB362BDB67769D3CC0Z/45/_/1778579316/66c4c9b2-868f-4ee4-8e90-16d6d0a261d6.jpg?width=1200","https://f.nooncdn.com/p/pzsku/Z3CBB362BDB67769D3CC0Z/45/_/1778579346/919313ad-f856-4ffc-84a4-ef0fd2a16760.jpg?width=1200","https://f.nooncdn.com/p/pzsku/Z3CBB362BDB67769D3CC0Z/45/_/1778579404/09f82c70-8ef7-4076-8d62-37be25cde7b4.jpg?width=1200","https://f.nooncdn.com/p/pzsku/Z3CBB362BDB67769D3CC0Z/45/_/1778579421/a882d3e4-8b28-4ecd-afbe-40f63ecd5287.jpg?width=1200"]'::jsonb, (select id from public.categories where slug = 'treatment-serums'), (select id from public.brands where slug = 'naturals'), 4.3, 311, 0, true, false, true, ARRAY['skin', 'care', 'treatment', 'serums', 'face']::text[]),
  ('Skinoren Anti Acne Treatment Cream,Original Freshness Cream to Lighten the Skin,Treat Pimples,Melasma and Acne 30g', 'skinoren-anti-acne-treatment-cream-original-freshness-cream-to-lighten', 'Contains the active ingredient azelaic acid. Can be used to treat acne. It treats melasma, dark spots caused by sunburn and freckles, and lightens the sensitive area. Works by attacking the bacteria which plays an essential part in causing acne. Reduces the growth of the harder outermost skin cells that block the pores of the skin to cause blackheads and whiteheads. Prevents clogging of skin pores and Fights pimples and blackheads,It regenerates skin cells and prevents the production of melanin pigment that is produced by the skin to darken the skin color', 'Contains the active ingredient azelaic acid. Can be used to treat acne.', 3.5, NULL, 'BHD', '["https://f.nooncdn.com/p/pzsku/Z2E9BCF2F12FAD37C3B77Z/45/1764906487/ce66f88b-b372-404b-9328-9c0d51204f02.jpg?width=1200","https://f.nooncdn.com/p/pzsku/Z2E9BCF2F12FAD37C3B77Z/45/1764906503/20e1cda4-092c-4a28-b9ba-6a548717f089.jpg?width=1200","https://f.nooncdn.com/p/pzsku/Z2E9BCF2F12FAD37C3B77Z/45/1764906513/4d30fec1-f898-4476-9632-f63b7d991309.jpg?width=1200","https://f.nooncdn.com/p/pzsku/Z2E9BCF2F12FAD37C3B77Z/45/1764906518/45df2a58-f47f-4d35-a011-c28c02ea1fcc.jpg?width=1200"]'::jsonb, (select id from public.categories where slug = 'treatment-serums'), (select id from public.brands where slug = 'skinoren'), 3.8, 18, 0, true, false, true, ARRAY['skin', 'care', 'treatment', 'serums', 'acne', 'blemish']::text[]),
  ('Vitamin C Brightening And Anti-Aging Facial Serum Orange 50ml', 'vitamin-c-brightening-and-anti-aging-facial-serum-orange-50ml', 'About the product: With a new improved formula, DR&middot;RASHEL Vitamin C face Serum is thin and highly effective. It will help fade sun spots & discolouration, refine skin texture, reduce wrinkle formation, and minimize existing wrinkles. It also has a highly concentrated base of pure vegan hyaluronic acid to plump skin cells and protect and restore them. Brightens and smoothes skin for a more radiant and youthful complexion. Powerful antioxidants neutralize free radicals to prevent and reverse sun damage and fade sun spots and discolouration. About the brand: DR RASHEL was founded in wealthy Dubai. Since its establishment in 2000, it has been the perfume brand deducing the acme of luxury, elegance and happiness by natural skincare and natural beauty. How to use: For best results, use twice a day. 1. Place a small amount of Intensive Spot Serum onto your hands and gently massage into trouble spots. 2. Use on the ends of your hair to help end split ends and breakage. 3. Use a small amount on the rest of your hair for fabulous shine and as a wonderful moisturizer.', 'With a new improved formula, DR&middot;RASHEL Vitamin C face Serum is thin and highly effective.', 1.7, NULL, 'BHD', '["https://f.nooncdn.com/p/pzsku/Z09D5D27DC1A404619DA6Z/45/_/1778591913/4605303f-6720-433d-81f0-bc8d0182342b.jpg?width=1200","https://f.nooncdn.com/p/pzsku/Z09D5D27DC1A404619DA6Z/45/_/1778591913/906df52e-7879-4a08-a30c-cb9591c6e0c8.jpg?width=1200","https://f.nooncdn.com/p/pzsku/Z09D5D27DC1A404619DA6Z/45/_/1778591913/63e82c9d-fa1f-4aae-a3d9-db4262552fd5.jpg?width=1200"]'::jsonb, (select id from public.categories where slug = 'treatment-serums'), (select id from public.brands where slug = 'dr-rashel'), 0, 0, 0, true, false, true, ARRAY['skin', 'care', 'treatment', 'serums', 'face']::text[]),
  ('Salicylic Acid Solution 30ml', 'salicylic-acid-solution-30ml', 'Combat acne with the Salicylic Acid 2% Solution from The Ordinary; a clarifying, blemish-fighting solution that gently sheds dead cells from the skin’s surface and calm redness and inflammation. Enriched with exfoliant Salicylic Acid, the solution penetrates the interior walls of congested pores to unclog and clear impurities, increases circulation and helps clear excess sebum and regulate production. Key ingredient Witch Hazel is a natural astringent and anti-inflammatory that aids in killing acne-causing bacteria and effectively protects the skin from oxidative stress and environmental aggressors such as smoke, pollution and UV light.', 'Combat acne with the Salicylic Acid 2% Solution from The Ordinary; a clarifying, blemish-fighting solution that gently sheds dead cells from…', 2.958, NULL, 'BHD', '["https://f.nooncdn.com/p/fb889ec50f784103a85817c4c97eadd1|pzsku/ZCC8C47CD614AB834B960Z/45/1771237452/4d06c896-6938-43b3-831b-0d697449c172.jpg?width=1200","https://f.nooncdn.com/p/fb889ec50f784103a85817c4c97eadd1|pzsku/ZCC8C47CD614AB834B960Z/45/1771237452/c3aac395-c06a-4df9-b9e5-fed7bcd557e9.jpg?width=1200","https://f.nooncdn.com/p/fb889ec50f784103a85817c4c97eadd1|pzsku/ZCC8C47CD614AB834B960Z/45/1771237452/dc807823-026b-49d6-90f9-2a2c0cb20822.jpg?width=1200","https://f.nooncdn.com/p/fb889ec50f784103a85817c4c97eadd1|pzsku/ZCC8C47CD614AB834B960Z/45/1771237452/9ec394c8-92cf-4162-a796-88c834c750c3.jpg?width=1200"]'::jsonb, (select id from public.categories where slug = 'treatment-serums'), (select id from public.brands where slug = 'the-ordinary'), 4.1, 823, 0, true, false, true, ARRAY['skin', 'care', 'treatment', 'serums', 'face']::text[]),
  ('Blemish Control Face Cleanser With 2% Salicylic Acid & Niacinamide For Acne & Blemish Prone Skin 236ml', 'blemish-control-face-cleanser-with-2-salicylic-acid-niacinamide-for-ac', 'CeraVe Blemish Control Cleanser is an anti blemish gel-to-foam refreshing gel-to-foam facial cleanser for blemish-prone skin, that helps to reduce the appearance of blemishes and blackheads, and removes excess oil while leaving the skin feeling soft and smooth. The formula penetrates pores to eliminate the cause of spots & blemishes, while protecting the skin’s natural barrier. It''s an acne face wash with salicylic acid which is a beta hydroxy acid (bha) that helps gently exfoliate and remove dead skin cells, reduce blackheads & the appearance of pores, and treats & prevents acne. CeraVe Blemish Control Cleanser contains 3 essential ceramides that are found naturally in the skin and make up 50% of the lipids in the skin barrier. All cerave products, formulated with three essential ceramides (1, 3, 6-ii)to help maintain the skin’s natural barrier. CeraVe skincare is developed with dermatologists and has products suitable for dry skin, sensitive skin, oily skin, acne-prone, and more.', 'CeraVe Blemish Control Cleanser is an anti blemish gel-to-foam refreshing gel-to-foam facial cleanser for blemish-prone skin, that helps to…', 7.3, NULL, 'BHD', '["https://f.nooncdn.com/p/pzsku/ZA44533D42E2B2D62C1EEZ/45/_/1778231322/5cd615be-b7da-4ff6-b4f5-8020368d3aff.jpg?width=1200","https://f.nooncdn.com/p/pzsku/ZA44533D42E2B2D62C1EEZ/45/_/1778231323/5815d20b-243b-4c27-aae7-ae880ce03fca.jpg?width=1200","https://f.nooncdn.com/p/pzsku/ZA44533D42E2B2D62C1EEZ/45/_/1778231323/ea2042c8-f2b7-4bf7-989f-d55c80cf4c9b.jpg?width=1200","https://f.nooncdn.com/p/pzsku/ZA44533D42E2B2D62C1EEZ/45/_/1778231323/055c302e-e103-4e4a-8b29-8c799858557f.jpg?width=1200"]'::jsonb, (select id from public.categories where slug = 'skin-cleansers'), (select id from public.brands where slug = 'cerave'), 4.4, 1763, 0, true, false, true, ARRAY['skin', 'care', 'cleansers', 'face', 'wash']::text[]),
  ('Glycolic Acid 7 % Toning Solution 240ml', 'glycolic-acid-7-toning-solution-240ml', 'Glycolic Acid 7% Exfoliating Toner (previously Glycolic Acid 7% Toning Solution) is an exfoliator that significantly smoothes skin texture and promotes the appearance of a more even skin tone, as well as more luminous skin, with regular use. It also reduces the appearance of lines and wrinkles. The water-based toner format is suited to daily use. It contains a 7% concentration of Glycolic acid - a well-studied alpha-hydroxy acid - and a plant-derived Tasmanian Pepperberry derivative, which varies in colour seasonally, and which may cause an apparent colour variation in the formula from time to time. This formula should not be used on sensitive, peeling or compromised skin. Please refer to the additional sun protection notes and other warnings in the provided directions. The pH of this formula is approximately 3.6. Glycolic Acid has a pKa of 3.6 and pKa is the most important aspect to consider in formulating with acids. pKa describes the acidity of a molecule. When pKa is close to pH, there is an ideal balance between salt and acidity, maximizing effectiveness of the acid and reducing irritation. The Ordinary Tip: The multi-functional formula can also be applied to the scalp, where it helps rebalance and reduces dryness by hydrating the scalp skin.', 'Glycolic Acid 7% Exfoliating Toner (previously Glycolic Acid 7% Toning Solution) is an exfoliator that significantly smoothes skin texture a…', 2.965, NULL, 'BHD', '["https://f.nooncdn.com/p/fb889ec50f784103a85817c4c97eadd1|pzsku/ZBCD56C67FE6156824974Z/45/1771237448/723353c1-a09e-4e6e-9bfe-52cb40cd8f7e.jpg?width=1200","https://f.nooncdn.com/p/fb889ec50f784103a85817c4c97eadd1|pzsku/ZBCD56C67FE6156824974Z/45/1771237448/c958b802-2303-4ac9-9c77-152167f4b976.jpg?width=1200","https://f.nooncdn.com/p/fb889ec50f784103a85817c4c97eadd1|pzsku/ZBCD56C67FE6156824974Z/45/1771237448/3fd45efc-72fc-41a5-8dab-9f956c68a4ad.jpg?width=1200","https://f.nooncdn.com/p/fb889ec50f784103a85817c4c97eadd1|pzsku/ZBCD56C67FE6156824974Z/45/1771237448/7eb68786-5d5a-49c7-bf7f-ea5cc2e5e467.jpg?width=1200"]'::jsonb, (select id from public.categories where slug = 'skin-cleansers'), (select id from public.brands where slug = 'the-ordinary'), 3.8, 6470, 0, true, false, true, ARRAY['skin', 'care', 'cleansers', 'toner']::text[]),
  ('Dermo Purifyer Cleansing Gel Pump Green 200ml', 'dermo-purifyer-cleansing-gel-pump-green-200ml', 'Don’t let skin impurity stop you from getting a healthy-looking skin. Eucerin’s DermoPURIFYER is a range of effective dermo cosmetic solutions for impure skin. Its products are designed to address four key factors pertaining impure skin: disrupted skin cell shedding, increased sebum production, increased bacteria proliferation and inflammation of the skin. Eucerin DermoPurifyer Oil Control Face Cleansing Gel is made without soap to help you gently yet effectively cleanse your face every day. Its formula contains 6% Ampho-Tensides that gently removes dirt, impurities, makeup and even excess sebum from your face for a beautifully cleansed, clear, fresh and supple skin. This cleansing face gel is formulated to be non-comedogenic, so it does not block or clog your pores. Additionally, the antibacterial property of the face wash effectively clears skin bacteria and prevents their growth. Eucerin DermoPurifyer Oil Control Face Cleanser is clinically and dermatologically proven to show good skin tolerability and efficacy on acne- and blemish-prone skin. It is also suitable for use during pregnancy.', 'Don’t let skin impurity stop you from getting a healthy-looking skin.', 7.95, NULL, 'BHD', '["https://f.nooncdn.com/p/pzsku/ZBEF629826C7F750166C8Z/45/_/1783068163/03b2b386-b670-4706-a831-f21676ec9735.jpg?width=1200","https://f.nooncdn.com/p/pzsku/ZBEF629826C7F750166C8Z/45/_/1779179128/f852ed0b-ea8e-4aff-aa38-77210148ecf1.jpg?width=1200","https://f.nooncdn.com/p/pzsku/ZBEF629826C7F750166C8Z/45/_/1779179128/af8cdbc2-1482-44d9-9998-a6343439ac67.jpg?width=1200","https://f.nooncdn.com/p/pzsku/ZBEF629826C7F750166C8Z/45/_/1779179127/8e966492-c76e-4e97-8288-6a57af6d7473.jpg?width=1200"]'::jsonb, (select id from public.categories where slug = 'skin-cleansers'), (select id from public.brands where slug = 'eucerin'), 4.1, 264, 0, true, false, true, ARRAY['skin', 'care', 'cleansers', 'cleansing', 'wipes']::text[]),
  ('Acne Creamy Wash, 4% Benzoyl Peroxide 170grams', 'acne-creamy-wash-4-benzoyl-peroxide-170grams', 'Gentle enough for everyday use and strong enough to combat the peskiest pimples, this daily wash contains 4% Benzoyl peroxide to clear acne at Lightning speed! Recommended by dermatologists, the creamy wash cleans and unclogs pores to clear existing breakouts. It can also help to prevent new blemishes from forming when used as part of a daily acne treatment routine. The creamy formula is balanced with emollients for a more gentle and hydrating daily Cleanse.', 'Gentle enough for everyday use and strong enough to combat the peskiest pimples, this daily wash contains 4% Benzoyl peroxide to clear acne…', 3.1, NULL, 'BHD', '["https://f.nooncdn.com/p/pzsku/Z57033373BC9C33A7040BZ/45/_/1776073396/03d9c196-408b-411b-be03-73f1164d69fe.jpg?width=1200","https://f.nooncdn.com/p/pzsku/Z57033373BC9C33A7040BZ/45/_/1776073397/ecd4ecc1-c904-4214-843f-52af8cc54b0c.jpg?width=1200"]'::jsonb, (select id from public.categories where slug = 'skin-cleansers'), (select id from public.brands where slug = 'panoxyl'), 3.9, 21, 0, true, false, true, ARRAY['skin', 'care', 'cleansers', 'face', 'wash']::text[]),
  ('Moroccan Rose Shea Sugar Scrub - 450g', 'moroccan-rose-shea-sugar-scrub-450g', 'Discover the secret to natural softness and radiance with Cosmo’s Moroccan Rose Shea Sugar Scrub, delivering unmatched renewal and deep hydration for your skin. Key Ingredients: Sugar granules: Gently exfoliate dead skin cells, help renew cells, and improve skin texture. Shea butter: Deeply moisturizes, nourishes the skin, and provides natural softness and elasticity. Moroccan rose extract: Refreshes the skin with a distinctive floral scent and protects it from damage thanks to antioxidants. Features and Benefits: Effectively exfoliates without causing dryness or irritation. Hydrates and nourishes the skin with concentrated natural shea butter. Enhances skin softness, leaving it more radiant and vibrant. Luxurious Moroccan rose fragrance adds a refreshing and soothing sensation during use. Improves skin texture and tone, making it look healthier and more beautiful. Suitable for all skin types and ideal for regular daily care. Give your skin a touch of luxury and radiance with Cosmo’s Moroccan Rose Shea Sugar Scrub.', 'Discover the secret to natural softness and radiance with Cosmo’s Moroccan Rose Shea Sugar Scrub, delivering unmatched renewal and deep hydr…', 1.6, NULL, 'BHD', '["https://f.nooncdn.com/p/pzsku/Z8B79F4E7FCDF6EFBF0CCZ/45/1766915501/8fb4a3e3-0c98-402b-978a-234d662b583a.jpg?width=1200"]'::jsonb, (select id from public.categories where slug = 'skin-cleansers'), (select id from public.brands where slug = 'cosmo'), 3.9, 21, 0, true, false, true, ARRAY['skin', 'care', 'cleansers', 'body', 'scrubs', 'polishes']::text[]),
  ('Effaclar Foaming Gel Clear 15ml', 'effaclar-foaming-gel-clear-15ml', 'Work the thick gel into a lather and it will produce a light non-irritating foam that is easy to rinse away. Apply every morning and evening by massaging in gently.', 'Work the thick gel into a lather and it will produce a light non-irritating foam that is easy to rinse away.', 90, NULL, 'BHD', '["https://f.nooncdn.com/p/pzsku/Z2A621B04DD17A24F8F05Z/45/_/1779791545/eaa6496a-1a5b-413c-b6e2-3255947f2824.jpg?width=1200"]'::jsonb, (select id from public.categories where slug = 'skin-cleansers'), (select id from public.brands where slug = 'beauty-gift'), 0, 0, 0, true, false, true, ARRAY['skin', 'care', 'cleansers', 'face', 'wash']::text[]),
  ('Acne Foaming Wash, Peroxide 10% Maximum Strength 5.5 Oz Packaging May Vary 5.5ounce', 'acne-foaming-wash-peroxide-10-maximum-strength-5-5-oz-packaging-may-va', 'New Formula. The new formulations create a better experience of a mild cleansing wash. The formulations were developed to be mild with a better lather and skin feel. The texture of the new formulations changed to better deliver against the desired properties of a mild cleansing wash. The formulations were developed to be mild, less paste-like products with a better lather and skin feel. Important information Safety Information For external use only.Do not use if you have very sensitive skin or if you are sensitive to benzoyl peroxide.When using this productavoid unnecessary sun exposure and use a sunscreen.keep away from eyes, lips and mouth.avoid contact with hair or dyed fabrics, including carpet and clothing which may be bleached by this product.with other topical acne medications, may have an increase in dryness or irritation to the skin. If this occurs, only one medication should be used, unless directed by ... Ingredients Cetearyl Alcohol, Cocamidopropyl Betaine, Glycerin, Glycolic Acid, Hydrogenated Castor Oil, Imidurea, Lactic Acid, Methylparaben, Mineral Oil, PEG-14M, Potassium Lauryl Sulfate, Purified Water, Sodium Hydroxide, Sodium Lauryl Sulfate, Sodium PCA, Titanium Dioxide, Zea Mays (Corn) Starch Directions Wet area to be cleansed.Apply acne wash and gently massage area for 1-2 minutes.Rinse thoroughly and pat dry.Because of excessive drying of the skin may occur, start with 1 application daily, then gradually increase to 2 or 3 times daily if needed or as directed by a doctor.If going outside, use a sunscreen. If irritation or sensitivity develops, discontinue use of both products and consult a doctor.', 'New Formula. The new formulations create a better experience of a mild cleansing wash.', 2.495, NULL, 'BHD', '["https://f.nooncdn.com/p/pzsku/Z94A8DB4C1EF5364ED104Z/45/_/1776073058/b42db454-221a-4d6d-a561-99976442c41d.jpg?width=1200","https://f.nooncdn.com/p/pzsku/Z94A8DB4C1EF5364ED104Z/45/_/1776073059/4ac8577d-6df1-4145-a7df-96a458bd80f6.jpg?width=1200","https://f.nooncdn.com/p/pzsku/Z94A8DB4C1EF5364ED104Z/45/_/1776073059/174415bb-cc64-4554-8c0a-525f946c141a.jpg?width=1200","https://f.nooncdn.com/p/pzsku/Z94A8DB4C1EF5364ED104Z/45/_/1776073059/cf632169-8975-4619-bfcc-9044771070cf.jpg?width=1200"]'::jsonb, (select id from public.categories where slug = 'skin-cleansers'), (select id from public.brands where slug = 'panoxyl'), 3.9, 3658, 0, true, false, true, ARRAY['skin', 'care', 'cleansers', 'face', 'wash']::text[]),
  ('Effaclar Purifying Foaming Gel Cleanser; Acne Face Wash For Women/Men; Dermatologically-Tested Skincare Treatment For Oily & Sensitive Skin 400ml', 'effaclar-purifying-foaming-gel-cleanser-acne-face-wash-for-women-men-d', 'La Roche Posay Effaclar Gel gently purifies oily skin without drying effects thanks to gentle cleansing agents rigorously selected to ensure good tolerance. It removes impurities and excess sebum, leaving the skin clean and refreshed. With anti-irritant La Roche-Posay thermal spring water and with Zinc to reduce sebum. Cleansing agents are selected for their high-efficacy action in eliminating impurities and excess sebum. The Effaclar Gel is specifically adapted and well-tolerated cleansing for acne-prone skin. Physiological pH - Alcohol-free.Non-comedogenic. Tested on acne-prone skin.', 'La Roche Posay Effaclar Gel gently purifies oily skin without drying effects thanks to gentle cleansing agents rigorously selected to ensure…', 9.695, NULL, 'BHD', '["https://f.nooncdn.com/p/pnsku/N11294410A/45/_/1778155560/18c6f228-6111-4e1f-9df2-49ede13a7b73.jpg?width=1200","https://f.nooncdn.com/p/pnsku/N11294410A/45/_/1778155562/8ed68224-c73a-4cb5-9d27-377b267d2e56.jpg?width=1200","https://f.nooncdn.com/p/pnsku/N11294410A/45/_/1778155563/4d4ee5f0-d980-493c-a608-1e29a09bed74.jpg?width=1200","https://f.nooncdn.com/p/pnsku/N11294410A/45/_/1778155564/55a94e9b-d1a9-4dd6-ac7c-59357f78c57f.jpg?width=1200"]'::jsonb, (select id from public.categories where slug = 'skin-cleansers'), (select id from public.brands where slug = 'la-roche-posay'), 4.6, 4796, 0, true, false, true, ARRAY['skin', 'care', 'cleansers', 'face', 'wash']::text[]),
  ('Glycolic Acid 7% Exfoliating Toner 240ml', 'glycolic-acid-7-exfoliating-toner-240ml', 'Product Information Brand: The Ordinary Item Form: Lotion (Liquid Toner) Skin Type: Normal (Not recommended for sensitive, peeling, or compromised skin) Product Benefits: Exfoliates for improved skin texture and tone Scent: Aloe Vera Size: 240 mL / 8.1 fl. oz About This Item ✨ Gentle Chemical Exfoliation Formulated with 7% Glycolic Acid to exfoliate the skin’s surface for a brighter, smoother, and more even complexion. 🌿 Aloe Vera Infusion Enriched with Aloe Vera to help soothe and calm the skin during exfoliation. 💧 Improves Skin Texture & Tone Regular use helps reduce dullness, improve skin clarity, and promote a healthy glow. ⚠ Not for Sensitive Skin Avoid use on sensitive, peeling, or compromised skin to prevent irritation. 🧴 Recommended Use Ideal for evening use as part of a skincare routine focused on softening and rejuvenation.', 'Product Information Brand: The Ordinary Item Form: Lotion (Liquid Toner) Skin Type: Normal (Not recommended for sensitive, peeling, or compr…', 2.838, NULL, 'BHD', '["https://f.nooncdn.com/p/fb889ec50f784103a85817c4c97eadd1|pzsku/ZA700766FEC26F413CB59Z/45/1771237487/8160cf4c-98f5-4329-8ead-2e09fa91a702.jpg?width=1200","https://f.nooncdn.com/p/fb889ec50f784103a85817c4c97eadd1|pzsku/ZA700766FEC26F413CB59Z/45/1771237487/3f21d7b1-19d4-41d4-9856-811f5f5d2dcc.jpg?width=1200","https://f.nooncdn.com/p/fb889ec50f784103a85817c4c97eadd1|pzsku/ZA700766FEC26F413CB59Z/45/1771237487/bd1af913-f8fd-4b21-aff9-37458b3190f5.jpg?width=1200","https://f.nooncdn.com/p/fb889ec50f784103a85817c4c97eadd1|pzsku/ZA700766FEC26F413CB59Z/45/1771237487/2267b468-9d84-4fd0-95c7-44a3bc6da6f2.jpg?width=1200"]'::jsonb, (select id from public.categories where slug = 'skin-cleansers'), (select id from public.brands where slug = 'the-ordinary'), 3.7, 199, 0, true, false, true, ARRAY['skin', 'care', 'cleansers', 'toner']::text[]),
  ('Skincare Anti-Aging, Dark Spot & Wrinkle Minimizing Toner Pads - Hydrating with Snail Mucin, Centella Asiatica, Niacinamide, Peptides - for Acne Marks & Hyperpigmentation - 100 Count', 'skincare-anti-aging-dark-spot-wrinkle-minimizing-toner-pads-hydrating', 'Use as both a daily toner or intensive treatment mask. For best results cleanse skin, apply pad evenly in gentle circular motions, wait 40-60 seconds, then apply moisturizer & continue with your skincare routine. Or leave on for up to 15 min as a spot-treating mask.', 'Use as both a daily toner or intensive treatment mask.', 4.506, NULL, 'BHD', '["https://f.nooncdn.com/p/386ae3cc97ba523a8e516a21894f7438|pzsku/Z560FFCE46642381E1C1DZ/45/1769752955/e7ffcdf5-0cff-43db-af08-e044007e9b2f.jpg?width=1200","https://f.nooncdn.com/p/386ae3cc97ba523a8e516a21894f7438|pzsku/Z560FFCE46642381E1C1DZ/45/1769752955/00bf6483-c851-4c50-9cd8-e3bc585661c3.jpg?width=1200","https://f.nooncdn.com/p/386ae3cc97ba523a8e516a21894f7438|pzsku/Z560FFCE46642381E1C1DZ/45/1769752955/fa8939b4-6ac7-4906-8f97-aefe8df14c35.jpg?width=1200","https://f.nooncdn.com/p/386ae3cc97ba523a8e516a21894f7438|pzsku/Z560FFCE46642381E1C1DZ/45/1769752955/1720e34c-6c55-4ff5-ba03-2b0191f6b747.jpg?width=1200"]'::jsonb, (select id from public.categories where slug = 'skin-cleansers'), (select id from public.brands where slug = 'jiyu'), 4.6, 10, 0, true, false, true, ARRAY['skin', 'care', 'cleansers', 'toner']::text[]),
  ('Dercos Energy + Stimulating and Anti Hair Loss Shampoo with Aminexil 200ml', 'dercos-energy-stimulating-and-anti-hair-loss-shampoo-with-aminexil-200', 'Vichy Dercos Energy + Stimulating Shampoo is enriched with Vichy''s patented molecule Aminexil,Niacinamide, AHA and VitaminE. Energy + Shampoo is designed to reduce the rate of hair loss, increase volume from the first application . Developed as a complement to hair-loss treatments, this shampoo is the only shampoo containing Aminexil. Hair is left feeling nourished, revitalized, and reinforced from root to tip, with an energized feel. Hair becomes stronger and more vigorous from roots to tips after 3 weeks. Clinically reduces hair loss after 6 weeks. Suitable for all hair types', 'Vichy Dercos Energy + Stimulating Shampoo is enriched with Vichy''s patented molecule Aminexil,Niacinamide, AHA and VitaminE.', 6.9, NULL, 'BHD', '["https://f.nooncdn.com/p/pzsku/ZE23E36371F9FDBF57CC4Z/45/_/1779344683/8d8948a7-072f-4cec-b1c4-edf571aac1dc.jpg?width=1200","https://f.nooncdn.com/p/pzsku/ZE23E36371F9FDBF57CC4Z/45/_/1779344684/7bcf6c65-f2c0-4dde-bc59-ef2ad006e3be.jpg?width=1200","https://f.nooncdn.com/p/pzsku/ZE23E36371F9FDBF57CC4Z/45/_/1779344683/b16d1c40-4ede-431a-8e25-b2cb2d564a5a.jpg?width=1200","https://f.nooncdn.com/p/pzsku/ZE23E36371F9FDBF57CC4Z/45/_/1779344684/5b2b8f69-3e94-4d65-96e6-4ab3fd4f33e3.jpg?width=1200"]'::jsonb, (select id from public.categories where slug = 'shampoos-conditioners'), (select id from public.brands where slug = 'vichy'), 0, 0, 0, true, false, true, ARRAY['hair', 'care', 'shampoos', 'conditioners']::text[]),
  ('Dercos Anti Dandruff Shampoo For Normal To Oily Hair For Men & Women 200ml', 'dercos-anti-dandruff-shampoo-for-normal-to-oily-hair-for-men-women-200', 'Vichy Dercos Anti Dandruff shampoo for Normal to oily hair. Suitable for daily use, this lightweight shampoo works to eliminate visible dandruff, providing anti-dandruff protection. Enriched with Selenium DS, the shampoo has an anti-fungal effect, helping to reduce redness and irritation on the scalp by combatting the growth of infection. Also infused with Ceramides, the formula helps to rebuild and strengthen the skin’s natural barriers, working to repair and protect the scalp while locking in moisture. This helps to combat itchiness and irritation, as well as offering antioxidant protection to shield the scalp from harmful environmental aggressors. Finally, Methanol leaves the hair purified and detoxified from root to tip, combatting excess oiliness and sebum production.You’ll be able to enjoy long-lasting comfort throughout the day from wash to wash. The formula is gentle enough to use daily or as often as needed.', 'Vichy Dercos Anti Dandruff shampoo for Normal to oily hair.', 6.9, NULL, 'BHD', '["https://f.nooncdn.com/p/pzsku/Z76C9D61E82659995635DZ/45/_/1779344991/6c56f367-56da-4ed9-ae32-3120319eb36f.jpg?width=1200","https://f.nooncdn.com/p/pzsku/Z76C9D61E82659995635DZ/45/_/1779344991/d5b23b4a-77f4-459e-8a7b-7fd8669e9fef.jpg?width=1200","https://f.nooncdn.com/p/pzsku/Z76C9D61E82659995635DZ/45/_/1779344991/04adc635-5b07-4e82-80db-c73faf4038d4.jpg?width=1200","https://f.nooncdn.com/p/pzsku/Z76C9D61E82659995635DZ/45/_/1779344991/93826b2c-e004-4621-82b4-48ddf786ccc6.jpg?width=1200"]'::jsonb, (select id from public.categories where slug = 'shampoos-conditioners'), (select id from public.brands where slug = 'vichy'), 4.6, 577, 0, true, false, true, ARRAY['hair', 'care', 'shampoos', 'conditioners']::text[]),
  ('Genesis Bain Hydra-Fortifiant Shampoo 250ml', 'genesis-bain-hydra-fortifiant-shampoo-250ml', 'About the product: Delicate fortifying shampoo for normal to oily, weakened hair that is prone to falling due to breakage from brushing Silicone-free. Gently removes sebum & pollution particles from scalp and hair. Provides oil-control. Prevents risk of hair-fall due to breakage from brushing. 97% less hair fall due to breakage from brushing*. About the brand: Since 1964, K&eacute;rastase has infused luxury with pioneering science to create exceptional hair care. Ingredients: A unique combination of Ginger Root and Edelweiss Native Cells: Ginger Root is known for its ability to protect against daily external aggressor. Edelweiss Native Cells is known in skincare for its antioxidant power and collagen preserving properties. The Edelweiss flower is capable to resist the most extreme conditions. How to use: 1. Apply to wet hair. Lather, Rinse, Repeat. 2. Massage. Rinse thoroughly. In case of contact with eyes, rinse them immediately and thoroughly.', 'Delicate fortifying shampoo for normal to oily, weakened hair that is prone to falling due to breakage from brushing Silicone-free.', 17.775, NULL, 'BHD', '["https://f.nooncdn.com/p/pnsku/N46787424A/45/_/1764242499/37facadf-20ac-42d8-a8e4-dd6ec4968167.jpg?width=1200","https://f.nooncdn.com/p/pnsku/N46787424A/45/_/1764242504/9d045279-dea0-4841-b8c7-786980a6dcc7.jpg?width=1200","https://f.nooncdn.com/p/pnsku/N46787424A/45/_/1764242500/6fc43515-9873-4789-8e02-50b0127b00ac.jpg?width=1200","https://f.nooncdn.com/p/pnsku/N46787424A/45/_/1764242500/178e278f-7a96-474c-b53e-2f193404a9c8.jpg?width=1200"]'::jsonb, (select id from public.categories where slug = 'shampoos-conditioners'), (select id from public.brands where slug = 'kerastase'), 4.4, 131, 0, true, false, true, ARRAY['hair', 'care', 'shampoos', 'conditioners']::text[]),
  ('Coconut Milk Shampoo Moisturizing Free Of Sulfates And Parabens 1000 Ml', 'coconut-milk-shampoo-moisturizing-free-of-sulfates-and-parabens-1000-m', 'Deeply cleanses hair while leaving it feeling soft Maintains hair freshness and prevents frizz The gentle formula ensures that it does not cause any scalp irritation Provides rich hydration to dry and damaged hair Argan is a key ingredient in this formula', 'Deeply cleanses hair while leaving it feeling soft Maintains hair freshness and prevents frizz The gentle formula ensures that it does not c…', 1.881, NULL, 'BHD', '["https://f.nooncdn.com/p/pzsku/ZAB1D1442021E14F5FAABZ/45/_/1716460420/c5243f09-0538-4268-8c81-913fab61e4f2.jpg?width=1200","https://f.nooncdn.com/p/pzsku/ZAB1D1442021E14F5FAABZ/45/_/1692193683/cb34d6f5-b068-4714-a5cc-28132a9b24e8.jpg?width=1200","https://f.nooncdn.com/p/pzsku/ZAB1D1442021E14F5FAABZ/45/_/1692193684/d6be7e7e-bcd6-469d-96cb-bea8728be8cc.jpg?width=1200"]'::jsonb, (select id from public.categories where slug = 'shampoos-conditioners'), (select id from public.brands where slug = 'cosmo'), 4.2, 319, 0, true, false, true, ARRAY['hair', 'care', 'shampoos', 'conditioners']::text[]),
  ('Absolut Repair Shampoo 300ml', 'absolut-repair-shampoo-300ml', 'Infused with GOLD QUINOA + PROTEIN, the professional formula of the Instant Resurfacing Shampoo immediately cleanses and restructures damaged hair, while leaving it with a lightweight touch. Hair is left shinier and smoother.', 'Infused with GOLD QUINOA + PROTEIN, the professional formula of the Instant Resurfacing Shampoo immediately cleanses and restructures damage…', 12.82, NULL, 'BHD', '["https://f.nooncdn.com/p/pzsku/ZC03044D79D9B5B60F741Z/45/_/1777287238/c33bafbb-c735-471f-a45d-aa998c0f4d9c.jpg?width=1200","https://f.nooncdn.com/p/pzsku/ZC03044D79D9B5B60F741Z/45/_/1773140165/6c8bde0c-62c8-46e1-83ee-524bcd1cd318.jpg?width=1200","https://f.nooncdn.com/p/pzsku/ZC03044D79D9B5B60F741Z/45/_/1773140165/da259f15-1b41-41fe-aa9d-12d3c3c6ea6b.jpg?width=1200","https://f.nooncdn.com/p/pzsku/ZC03044D79D9B5B60F741Z/45/_/1773140165/2f67cb17-b7de-4e40-884f-92562b6d6937.jpg?width=1200"]'::jsonb, (select id from public.categories where slug = 'shampoos-conditioners'), (select id from public.brands where slug = 'l-ore-al-professionnel'), 4.6, 504, 0, true, false, true, ARRAY['hair', 'care', 'shampoos', 'conditioners']::text[]),
  ('No. 4P Blonde Enhancer Toning Shampoo Lavender 250ml', 'no-4p-blonde-enhancer-toning-shampoo-lavender-250ml', 'Highly concentrated purple shampoo cleanses, tones, and repairs while keeping hair hydrated from roots to ends. Sulfate-free formula creates a rich lather to neutralize brassiness and boost brightness after one use for all blonde, lightened, and grey hair. Natural or stylist-created, root-to-tip or balayage, every client can benefit using this as part of their Blonde Maintenance Routine for the best blonde yet. Key benefits: • 3x brighter hair* • Neutralizes yellow tones • Maintains hydrated hair *Compared to top purple shampoos in premium retail & salon, 2022 How to use: 1. Distribute evenly between palms first. 2. Apply to wet hair and lather fully. 3. Leave on for 1-3 minutes. (For more intense toning, leave on up to 5 minutes.) 4. Rinse well and condition. For optimal brightening and hydration, use No.5P Blonde Enhancer Toning Conditioner from roots to ends. When to use: Use as needed to neutralize unwanted brassiness. Natural blondes and greys: Every 1-2 washes Sun-kissed blondes: Every other wash Textured blondes: Every other wash Damaged blondes Once a week Platinum blondes: Every 2-3 washes *No two blondes are created equal. Timing & frequency may vary. Ingredients: Water (Aqua/Eau), Sodium C14-16 Olefin Sulfonate, Cocamidopropyl Betaine, Glycerin, Sodium Cocoamphoacetate, Sodium Chloride, Acrylates Copolymer, Betaine, Phenoxyethanol, Fragrance (Parfum), Polyquaternium-7, Bis-Aminopropyl Diglycol Dimaleate, Guar Hydroxypropyltrimonium Chloride, Ethylhexylglycerin, Hexyl Cinnamal, Limonene, Citric Acid, Sodium Benzoate, Acid Violet 43 (Cl 60730)', 'Highly concentrated purple shampoo cleanses, tones, and repairs while keeping hair hydrated from roots to ends.', 9.96, NULL, 'BHD', '["https://f.nooncdn.com/p/pzsku/Z30E5042089C3C8D04384Z/45/_/1779179083/1e76f7ef-c1f1-47ce-824d-9f775755ff41.jpg?width=1200","https://f.nooncdn.com/p/pzsku/Z30E5042089C3C8D04384Z/45/_/1779179083/27f116d2-871a-4f03-9d3c-7aab856aab30.jpg?width=1200","https://f.nooncdn.com/p/pzsku/Z30E5042089C3C8D04384Z/45/_/1779179084/388cb7c4-e3d6-4a18-9820-383ed17748ee.jpg?width=1200","https://f.nooncdn.com/p/pzsku/Z30E5042089C3C8D04384Z/45/_/1779179084/d6e4b555-90ba-4e0f-bfda-d14ebe2c0209.jpg?width=1200"]'::jsonb, (select id from public.categories where slug = 'shampoos-conditioners'), (select id from public.brands where slug = 'olaplex'), 4.1, 46, 0, true, false, true, ARRAY['hair', 'care', 'shampoos', 'conditioners']::text[]),
  ('Pro-V Daily Care 2 In 1 Shampoo Healthier Hair With Every Wash white 1litre', 'pro-v-daily-care-2-in-1-shampoo-healthier-hair-with-every-wash-white-1', 'Pantene Pro-V Daily Care 2in1 Shampoo, Healthier Hair with Every Wash, 1 L. Struggling with greasy hair every day? It’s the right time to start using a cleansing shampoo that helps remove dirt, oil and product build-up. Pantene Pro-V Daily Care 2in1 Shampoo makes greasy hair a thing of the past. The nourishing blend of Pantene’s pro-vitamins technology helps achieve thicker and stronger hair in 14 days*. The shampoo’s effective formula cleanses hair and removes styling build-up to deliver healthy-looking, cleaner and shinier hair from root to tip with every wash. Pantene’s 2in1 nourishing system provides deep moisturization and helps repair hair to ensure protection against damage. If you’re looking to further nourish your hair, use Pantene Pro-V Daily Care Oil Replacement Leave-On Cream after the daily shampoo for healthier and cleaner hair every day. Shop the entire range of Pantene’s daily care routine – 1) Shampoo 2) Conditioner 3) Oil Replacement Leave-On Cream 4) 3-Minute Miracle Conditioner. This hair care regimen provides everything you need to deliver strength and nourishment to your hair every day. Also explore Pantene’s other hair care collections to address specific hair concerns – 1) Goodbye Frizz 2) Anti-Hair Fall 3) Milky Damage Repair 4) Smooth and Silky 5) Daily Care, and more. *strength against styling damage vs non-conditioning shampoo', 'Pantene Pro-V Daily Care 2in1 Shampoo, Healthier Hair with Every Wash, 1 L.', 2.799, NULL, 'BHD', '["https://f.nooncdn.com/p/pnsku/N11265609A/45/_/1744711391/b80d420e-d195-4b9f-9b20-4e8e536decd5.jpg?width=1200","https://f.nooncdn.com/p/pnsku/N11265609A/45/_/1744711392/d0cae99a-d0ef-40b3-94d7-866a79eb89e6.jpg?width=1200","https://f.nooncdn.com/p/pnsku/N11265609A/45/_/1744711395/08479f83-7d69-443b-8cc9-b9c1438f5e60.jpg?width=1200","https://f.nooncdn.com/p/pnsku/N11265609A/45/_/1744711406/966ee116-4b65-4659-9ffa-af01f56f4100.jpg?width=1200"]'::jsonb, (select id from public.categories where slug = 'shampoos-conditioners'), (select id from public.brands where slug = 'pantene'), 4.6, 441, 0, true, false, true, ARRAY['hair', 'care', 'shampoos', 'conditioners']::text[]),
  ('Dercos Anti Dandruff Shampoo For Dry Hair 200ml', 'dercos-anti-dandruff-shampoo-for-dry-hair-200ml', 'Vichy Dercos Anti Dandruff Shampoo for Dry hair. Suitable for daily use, this lightweight shampoo works to eliminate visible dandruff, providing anti-dandruff protection. Enriched with Selenium DS, the shampoo has an anti-fungal effect, helping to reduce redness and irritation on the scalp by combatting the growth of infection. Also infused with Ceramides, the formula helps to rebuild and strengthen the skin’s natural barriers, working to repair and protect the scalp while locking in moisture. This helps to combat itchiness and irritation, as well as offering antioxidant protection to shield the scalp from harmful environmental aggressors. Finally, Methanol leaves the hair purified and detoxified from root to tip, combatting excess oiliness and sebum production.You’ll be able to enjoy long-lasting comfort throughout the day from wash to wash. The formula is gentle enough to use daily or as often as needed.', 'Vichy Dercos Anti Dandruff Shampoo for Dry hair.', 6.9, NULL, 'BHD', '["https://f.nooncdn.com/p/pzsku/Z653DD95D775ADAB08463Z/45/_/1779715625/eb0ba1a5-c020-4a6f-95ce-d7427b3eb86d.jpg?width=1200","https://f.nooncdn.com/p/pzsku/Z653DD95D775ADAB08463Z/45/_/1779715625/c56c569b-bc81-4e62-aa2d-aecae493bea9.jpg?width=1200","https://f.nooncdn.com/p/pzsku/Z653DD95D775ADAB08463Z/45/_/1779715625/30c76169-5267-47a5-812f-06c190aaa13f.jpg?width=1200","https://f.nooncdn.com/p/pzsku/Z653DD95D775ADAB08463Z/45/_/1779715625/4fb52649-2665-470a-ab6e-78595198449f.jpg?width=1200"]'::jsonb, (select id from public.categories where slug = 'shampoos-conditioners'), (select id from public.brands where slug = 'vichy'), 0, 0, 0, true, false, true, ARRAY['hair', 'care', 'shampoos', 'conditioners']::text[]),
  ('Genesis Fondant Reinforcatuer Conditioner 200ml', 'genesis-fondant-reinforcatuer-conditioner-200ml', 'About the product: Lightweight fortifying conditioner for weakened hair that is prone to falling due to breakage from brushing. For daily use. Anti Hair-fall Fortifying conditioner for weakened hair, prone to falling due to breakage. This creamy formula offers anti-breakage action with the most lightweight finish. It helps restore the fiber and reinforces its natural resistance to reduce the risk of hair-fall due to breakage. Enriched with the combination of Edelweiss Native Cells and Ginger Root, it instantly smoothes, strengthens and softens the fiber while providing deep nutrition without weighing down the hair. Hair is uniform, shiny and stronger. About the brand: Since 1964, K&eacute;rastase has infused luxury with pioneering science to create exceptional hair care. Ingredients: A unique combination of Ginger Root and Edelweiss Native Cells: Ginger Root is known for its ability to protect against daily external aggressor. Edelweiss Native Cells is known in skincare for its antioxidant power and collagen preserving properties. The Edelweiss flower is capable to resist the most extreme conditions. How to use: 1. Apply a hazelnut sized amount on washed and towel-dried hair. 2. Massage through mid-lengths and ends, avoiding roots to ensure lightweight volume. 3. Leave in for 2 to 3 minutes. 4. Emulsify and rinse thoroughly. Pro Tip: This conditioner is gentle enough for daily usage and is ideal when paired with the Bain Hydra-Fortifiant or Bain Nutri-Fortifiant.', 'Lightweight fortifying conditioner for weakened hair that is prone to falling due to breakage from brushing. For daily use.', 21.01, NULL, 'BHD', '["https://f.nooncdn.com/p/v1660629980/N35170746A_1.jpg?width=1200","https://f.nooncdn.com/p/v1589273276/N35170746A_3.jpg?width=1200","https://f.nooncdn.com/p/v1589273275/N35170746A_2.jpg?width=1200"]'::jsonb, (select id from public.categories where slug = 'shampoos-conditioners'), (select id from public.brands where slug = 'kerastase'), 4.7, 342, 0, true, false, true, ARRAY['hair', 'care', 'shampoos', 'conditioners']::text[]),
  ('Elvive Fall Resist Conditioner 360ml Packaging may vary', 'elvive-fall-resist-conditioner-360ml-packaging-may-vary', 'L''Oréal Elvive Full Resist Reinforcing Fragile Hair Conditioner with Biotin, for Hair Fall Get your full hair workout. Get your full hair workout with our Full Resist regime. Our reinforcing formula enriched with works in affinity with the hair fiber from root to tip. Ideal for weak and fragile hair types which have a tendency to break and fall*. No need to worry about excessive hair breakage or fall out again. The results: Up to 98.8% less breakage* when brushing. Scalp feels healthier, hair breaks less* and feels reinforced**. Suitable for men and women. Get your full hair workout! Pollution, seasonal change, daily brushing and styling… Your hair feels weaker, thinner and tends to break and fall more easily. Rebuild your hair strength with our Full Resist regime! Our reinforcing formula charged with supplements [ biotin + vitamin B5 + arginine] works in affinity with the hair fiber from root to tip. Day after day, scalp feels healthier, hair breaks less* and feels more reinforced. How to use: • Apply on wet hair, focusing on lengths. Leave for one minute then rinse. • Complete your fragile hair routine with our Brush Resist Cream, giving extra protection from breakage due to brushing.', 'L''Oréal Elvive Full Resist Reinforcing Fragile Hair Conditioner with Biotin, for Hair Fall Get your full hair workout.', 2.68, NULL, 'BHD', '["https://f.nooncdn.com/p/pzsku/Z605B7E84A1A89840FFFEZ/45/_/1776409946/eca04c2b-7ace-43fa-9188-6a904643efb7.jpg?width=1200","https://f.nooncdn.com/p/pzsku/Z605B7E84A1A89840FFFEZ/45/_/1776409946/d5ad76f0-7866-40a3-aa1d-6498e2d7123c.jpg?width=1200","https://f.nooncdn.com/p/pzsku/Z605B7E84A1A89840FFFEZ/45/_/1776409947/8b966000-9875-4ab7-a8aa-4efb25ba71cc.jpg?width=1200","https://f.nooncdn.com/p/pzsku/Z605B7E84A1A89840FFFEZ/45/_/1776409946/3ea4a6c3-a15b-47a5-8ece-7d26e055be9f.jpg?width=1200"]'::jsonb, (select id from public.categories where slug = 'shampoos-conditioners'), (select id from public.brands where slug = 'l-oreal-paris'), 4.5, 248, 0, true, false, true, ARRAY['hair', 'care', 'shampoos', 'conditioners']::text[]),
  ('Elvive Moisturizing Conditioner for Dehydrated Hair - 360 ml', 'elvive-moisturizing-conditioner-for-dehydrated-hair-360-ml', '"L''OREAL PARIS Elvive Hyaluron Moisture 72H Moisture Sealing Conditioner 360 ml Elvive Hyaluron Conditioner is specifically designed to be gentle versus regular adult products. Boosts natural shine for silky smooth and healthy-looking hair. It offers the best quality results. Leaves hair soft, shiny and manageable and feeling healthy. Damaged, dehydrated hair? Try NEW Elvive Hydra Hyaluronic Moisture Locking Conditioner with Hyaluronic Acid, from L''Oréal Paris. The formula, infused with Hyaluronic Acid, weightlessly coats hair to keep it feeling hydrated for up to 72 hours. The results? Hair looks visibly plumped, bouncy and shiny. Our scientifically proven skincare inspired formula helps tackle dehydrated, dry and damaged hair, the first sign of hair damage. How to use: • Start by applying on damp hair, focusing on lengths and ends. Leave for one minute, then rinse. • For best results, use after the L''Oréal Paris Elvive Hyaluron Moisture Shampoo.', '"L''OREAL PARIS Elvive Hyaluron Moisture 72H Moisture Sealing Conditioner 360 ml Elvive Hyaluron Conditioner is specifically designed to be g…', 2.2, NULL, 'BHD', '["https://f.nooncdn.com/p/pzsku/Z95074A2AB32FE1859CDEZ/45/_/1781597160/ecb3e056-475b-4772-8cfa-9ef87916e8a8.jpg?width=1200","https://f.nooncdn.com/p/pzsku/Z95074A2AB32FE1859CDEZ/45/_/1781597160/1d269adf-d9ab-4b03-a60d-e31e67c4c3a7.jpg?width=1200","https://f.nooncdn.com/p/pzsku/Z95074A2AB32FE1859CDEZ/45/_/1781597160/1c341fe7-eb0a-4df0-9b4a-d202518d9f24.jpg?width=1200","https://f.nooncdn.com/p/pzsku/Z95074A2AB32FE1859CDEZ/45/_/1781597160/a4cf87f5-b3f4-4efd-a6a9-cda5ee58035d.jpg?width=1200"]'::jsonb, (select id from public.categories where slug = 'shampoos-conditioners'), (select id from public.brands where slug = 'l-oreal-paris'), 0, 0, 0, true, false, true, ARRAY['hair', 'care', 'shampoos', 'conditioners']::text[]),
  ('Pro-V Anti Hair Fall Shampoo Strengthens Fragile Strands 1litre', 'pro-v-anti-hair-fall-shampoo-strengthens-fragile-strands-1litre', 'Pantene Pro-V Daily Care 2in1 Shampoo, Healthier Hair with Every Wash, 1 L. Don’t let hair fall deter you from getting healthy hair. Experience strong and beautiful locks with Pantene Pro-V Anti-Hair Fall Shampoo – made to reduce hair fall* and deliver thicker, stronger hair in 14 days*. Harnessing the power of Pantene’s pro-vitamins formula, this hair fall control shampoo thoroughly cleanses hair to wash away impurities and strengthen hair against damage caused by frequent styling procedures. Pantene’s nourishing technology makes hair more resilient and helps achieve beautifully stronger, nourished and healthier hair wash after wash. For even deeper nourishment and heat protection up to 230°C, try our Anti-Hair Fall Nourishing Oil Replacement Leave-On Cream. With Pantene Pro-V’s Complete Anti-Hair Fall range, experience showers without any fallen hair strands – 1) Shampoo 2) Conditioner 3) Oil Replacement Leave-On Cream 4) Nourishing Hair Mask 5) 3-Minute Miracle Conditioner. Also explore Pantene’s other hair care collections to address specific hair concerns – 1) Goodbye Frizz 2) Anti-Hair Fall 3) Milky Damage Repair 4) Smooth and Silky 5) Daily Care, and more. *due to breakage *strength against styling damage vs non-conditioning shampoo alone.', 'Pantene Pro-V Daily Care 2in1 Shampoo, Healthier Hair with Every Wash, 1 L. Don’t let hair fall deter you from getting healthy hair.', 1.9, NULL, 'BHD', '["https://f.nooncdn.com/p/pnsku/N11265608A/45/_/1744710308/676fea25-b8e7-450c-8e39-d9d5c16b6bc9.jpg?width=1200","https://f.nooncdn.com/p/pnsku/N11265608A/45/_/1744710323/a9757967-43b6-4323-b7d9-bd38919b3405.jpg?width=1200","https://f.nooncdn.com/p/pnsku/N11265608A/45/_/1744710309/e13cdefd-7ecb-44d3-aef8-5d96c009299e.jpg?width=1200","https://f.nooncdn.com/p/pnsku/N11265608A/45/_/1744710311/4ae864c0-51fb-4a10-b148-4bf9b7b5c5b2.jpg?width=1200"]'::jsonb, (select id from public.categories where slug = 'hair-scalp-treatments'), (select id from public.brands where slug = 'pantene'), 4.7, 538, 0, true, false, true, ARRAY['hair', 'care', 'scalp', 'treatments', 'masks']::text[]),
  ('No. 5P Blonde Enhancer Toning Conditioner Lavender Lavender 250ml', 'no-5p-blonde-enhancer-toning-conditioner-lavender-lavender-250ml', 'Highly-moisturizing, reparative conditioner for all hair types that leaves hair easy to manage, shiny and healthier with each use. Colour-safe, leaves hair stronger than ever, and benefits all hair types and textures. It is color-safe and will strengthen and leave your hair stronger than ever. Free from dea and aldehydes', 'Highly-moisturizing, reparative conditioner for all hair types that leaves hair easy to manage, shiny and healthier with each use.', 12.596, NULL, 'BHD', '["https://f.nooncdn.com/p/pzsku/ZCE4FF7B1B7E27D25D817Z/45/_/1777376118/de00c20d-97ef-40cf-85f0-4eb9dacee547.jpg?width=1200","https://f.nooncdn.com/p/pzsku/ZCE4FF7B1B7E27D25D817Z/45/_/1777376118/755fba79-1dc1-4fba-b282-82b27c23ac78.jpg?width=1200","https://f.nooncdn.com/p/pzsku/ZCE4FF7B1B7E27D25D817Z/45/_/1777376118/f4212946-fb27-4178-acbe-00f72726f3d9.jpg?width=1200","https://f.nooncdn.com/p/pzsku/ZCE4FF7B1B7E27D25D817Z/45/_/1777376118/164fb7ba-ce0c-47fd-823f-ccf52f14395c.jpg?width=1200"]'::jsonb, (select id from public.categories where slug = 'shampoos-conditioners'), (select id from public.brands where slug = 'olaplex'), 4.7, 9, 0, true, false, true, ARRAY['hair', 'care', 'shampoos', 'conditioners']::text[]),
  ('Sulfate Free Conditioner with Keratin and Protein 1000ml 1000ml', 'sulfate-free-conditioner-with-keratin-and-protein-1000ml-1000ml', 'The Sulfate-Free Hair Conditioner with Protein & Keratin (1000 ml) is specially formulated to provide deep hydration and silky softness after protein and keratin treatments. Enriched with natural oils like macadamia oil, coconut oil, sweet almond oil, and argan oil, it nourishes hair from roots to ends, helping repair damage and reduce split ends. Free from sulfates, parabens, silicones, and sodium chloride, it is perfect for chemically treated or straightened hair.', 'The Sulfate-Free Hair Conditioner with Protein & Keratin (1000 ml) is specially formulated to provide deep hydration and silky softness afte…', 3.777, NULL, 'BHD', '["https://f.nooncdn.com/p/pnsku/N52056782A/45/_/1773300123/87a619a1-8cc3-48b6-971e-4b0b4e0e4792.jpg?width=1200","https://f.nooncdn.com/p/pnsku/N52056782A/45/_/1773300124/32205a08-a5ca-4832-801b-748e4f9362da.jpg?width=1200","https://f.nooncdn.com/p/pnsku/N52056782A/45/_/1773300123/c2a117ad-e121-47ca-918f-713f834d1b68.jpg?width=1200"]'::jsonb, (select id from public.categories where slug = 'shampoos-conditioners'), (select id from public.brands where slug = 'oplus'), 4.5, 352, 0, true, false, true, ARRAY['hair', 'care', 'shampoos', 'conditioners']::text[]),
  ('Hair Conditioner Almond Oil & Honey 300ml', 'hair-conditioner-almond-oil-honey-300ml', 'Containing our exclusive blend of Crude Shea Butter, Almond Oil & Honey, this unique nourishing moisture Hair Conditioner deeply nourishes, repairs and protects your hair and scalp from root to tip. An ultra-hydration daily conditioner that deeply replenishes stressed out, depleted hair strands with essential vitamins and minerals provided by Almond Oil. Combined with pure Shea Butter & Honey, hair is highly protected against future breakage. Ideal for dry and damaged hair, it looks healthier and radiant for long term results', 'Containing our exclusive blend of Crude Shea Butter, Almond Oil & Honey, this unique nourishing moisture Hair Conditioner deeply nourishes,…', 3.16, NULL, 'BHD', '["https://f.nooncdn.com/p/pnsku/N43655418A/45/_/1767607769/bba0c56d-0e06-45a3-b601-d38eb42601fc.jpg?width=1200","https://f.nooncdn.com/p/v1610860977/N43655418A_2.jpg?width=1200","https://f.nooncdn.com/p/v1610860977/N43655418A_3.jpg?width=1200"]'::jsonb, (select id from public.categories where slug = 'shampoos-conditioners'), (select id from public.brands where slug = 'shea-miracles'), 4.3, 57, 0, true, false, true, ARRAY['hair', 'care', 'shampoos', 'conditioners']::text[]),
  ('Hair Fall Defense Conditioner Clear 180ml', 'hair-fall-defense-conditioner-clear-180ml', 'Antioxidants keep the hair strong and healthy. Deeply moisturizes hair and protects them from getting damaged. Potent formula helps to boost circulation and relax muscles', 'Antioxidants keep the hair strong and healthy. Deeply moisturizes hair and protects them from getting damaged.', 1.295, NULL, 'BHD', '["https://f.nooncdn.com/p/pnsku/N29386500A/45/_/1756539429/7c96283b-5f1b-499b-80e5-0f12d0c156dd.jpg?width=1200","https://f.nooncdn.com/p/v1668085695/N29386500A_2.jpg?width=1200","https://f.nooncdn.com/p/v1668085695/N29386500A_3.jpg?width=1200"]'::jsonb, (select id from public.categories where slug = 'shampoos-conditioners'), (select id from public.brands where slug = 'cream-silk'), 4.6, 269, 0, true, false, true, ARRAY['hair', 'care', 'shampoos', 'conditioners']::text[]),
  ('Pro-V Moisture Renewal Conditioner Moisturizes Driest Hair 360ml', 'pro-v-moisture-renewal-conditioner-moisturizes-driest-hair-360ml', 'Pantene Pro-V Moisture Renewal Conditioner, Moisturizes the Driest Hair, 360 ml. We all love styling our hair. But often, the drying and styling procedures take a toll on our hair, leaving it looking extremely dry and dehydrated. Thanks to Pantene Pro-V Moisture Renewal Conditioner, you can now moisturize even the driest of the hair strands. With its pro-v technology, the hair conditioner also protects and strengthens hair against styling damage. Pantene’s nourishing technology locks in moisture in your hair to nourish it from root to tip for beautiful hair that looks and feels healthier and smoother. If you’re looking to further nourish your hair, use Pantene Pro-V Moisture Renewal Oil Replacement Leave-On Cream after shampooing for deeply moisturized hair. Shop the entire range of Pantene’s Moisture Renewal products – 1) Shampoo 2) Conditioner 3) Oil Replacement Leave-On Cream. This hair care regimen provides everything you need to moisturize the driest of the hair. Also explore Pantene’s other hair care collections to address specific hair concerns – 1) Goodbye Frizz 2) Anti-Hair Fall 3) Milky Damage Repair 4) Smooth and Silky 5) Daily Care, and more.', 'Pantene Pro-V Moisture Renewal Conditioner, Moisturizes the Driest Hair, 360 ml. We all love styling our hair.', 0.988, NULL, 'BHD', '["https://f.nooncdn.com/p/pnsku/N11265597A/45/_/1714072310/31bd09a4-31bd-4644-a122-0f199d00d135.jpg?width=1200","https://f.nooncdn.com/p/pnsku/N11265597A/45/_/1713868752/313799b9-ccf2-47a6-8e41-6f4f3ac1669c.jpg?width=1200","https://f.nooncdn.com/p/pnsku/N11265597A/45/_/1713868752/7a4bc955-0538-4076-9657-f8d10d84e9ae.jpg?width=1200","https://f.nooncdn.com/p/pnsku/N11265597A/45/_/1713868751/e9be75c2-f4bb-4e2a-a44a-4928d02d6c0b.jpg?width=1200"]'::jsonb, (select id from public.categories where slug = 'hair-scalp-treatments'), (select id from public.brands where slug = 'pantene'), 4.6, 347, 0, true, false, true, ARRAY['hair', 'care', 'scalp', 'treatments', 'masks']::text[]),
  ('Hair Concealer Filling Cream for Bald Spots Thinning Hair Waterproof SweatProof Scalp Coverage Natural Root TouchUp Cream for Men Women 30ml', 'hair-concealer-filling-cream-for-bald-spots-thinning-hair-waterproof-s', 'Online shopping for BATCI. Trusted Shipping to Riyadh, Jeddah and all KSA ✓ Great Prices ✓ Secure Shopping ✓ 100% Contactless ✓ Easy Free Returns ✓ Cash on Delivery. Shop Now', 'Online shopping for BATCI. Trusted Shipping to Riyadh, Jeddah and all KSA ✓ Great Prices ✓ Secure Shopping ✓ 100% Contactless ✓ Easy Free Re…', 19, NULL, 'BHD', '["https://f.nooncdn.com/p/pzsku/ZB21F18F2459A0E2A1975Z/45/1766238310/fe027514-1653-4e11-9011-3b2a264e687f.jpg?width=1200","https://f.nooncdn.com/p/pzsku/ZB21F18F2459A0E2A1975Z/45/1766237483/987a2423-e014-4a6d-86d3-0b73484e5f8b.jpg?width=1200","https://f.nooncdn.com/p/pzsku/ZB21F18F2459A0E2A1975Z/45/1766237483/042d87d0-e021-479c-b1b2-82dd491b1a71.jpg?width=1200","https://f.nooncdn.com/p/pzsku/ZB21F18F2459A0E2A1975Z/45/1766237483/f1a9f6bf-f2e0-48f5-ab62-bf2b39fea80c.jpg?width=1200"]'::jsonb, (select id from public.categories where slug = 'hair-color'), (select id from public.brands where slug = 'batci'), 3.9, 70, 0, true, false, true, ARRAY['hair', 'care', 'color', 'root', 'cover', 'ups']::text[]),
  ('Permanent Hair Coloration 7-0 Natural Dark Blonde', 'permanent-hair-coloration-7-0-natural-dark-blonde', 'Schwarzkopf Creme Supreme Bonding Color with HAPTIQ System protects your hair from damage in every step of the coloring process. This 3-step system includes a Pre-Serum that creates smoother micro-bonds, the Bonding Color cream that protects hair while coloring, and a Bonding Mask that envelopes hair with a protective layer. Achieve beautiful and even color results with 100% grey coverage in a natural dark blonde shade.', 'Schwarzkopf Creme Supreme Bonding Color with HAPTIQ System protects your hair from damage in every step of the coloring process.', 5.685, NULL, 'BHD', '["https://f.nooncdn.com/p/pzsku/Z7E03E8F5BA65145DAFACZ/45/1756050070/49fb513a-1f9c-4865-8113-746a48db0deb.jpg?width=1200","https://f.nooncdn.com/p/pzsku/Z7E03E8F5BA65145DAFACZ/45/1756050069/8d94a69a-9a08-4503-a1a2-bce3788fdccb.jpg?width=1200"]'::jsonb, (select id from public.categories where slug = 'hair-color'), (select id from public.brands where slug = 'schwarzkopf-creme-supreme'), 4.6, 16, 0, true, false, true, ARRAY['hair', 'care', 'color', 'chemical', 'dyes']::text[]),
  ('Permanent Hair Coloration 6-88 Intensive Red', 'permanent-hair-coloration-6-88-intensive-red', 'Schwarzkopf Creme Supreme Bonding Color with the advanced HAPTIQ System protects your hair from damage in every step of the coloring process. The 3-step system includes a Pre-Serum to strengthen micro-bonds, a Bonding Color Cream that nourishes while coloring, and a Bonding Mask for intensive aftercare. The result is a radiant, even red color with up to 100% grey coverage.', 'Schwarzkopf Creme Supreme Bonding Color with the advanced HAPTIQ System protects your hair from damage in every step of the coloring process…', 6.365, NULL, 'BHD', '["https://f.nooncdn.com/p/pzsku/Z4213D41ECC56732BAD7FZ/45/1755629508/61df7fe6-c78f-407b-b779-0bab09abed17.jpg?width=1200","https://f.nooncdn.com/p/pzsku/Z4213D41ECC56732BAD7FZ/45/1755629509/875fc8cf-4dce-44be-bc5f-959f51b37513.jpg?width=1200"]'::jsonb, (select id from public.categories where slug = 'hair-color'), (select id from public.brands where slug = 'schwarzkopf-creme-supreme'), 4.2, 20, 0, true, false, true, ARRAY['hair', 'care', 'color', 'chemical', 'dyes']::text[]),
  ('Hair Color Stick Light Brown, Grey Root Cover Up Instant Hair Root Touch-Up Stick, Temporary Hair Dye For Natural Gray Coverage Long-Lasting Moisturizing Formula With Plant Extracts 20g', 'hair-color-stick-light-brown-grey-root-cover-up-instant-hair-root-touc', 'Helps cover gray roots quickly for a natural-looking result.. Stick design allows precise and mess-free touch-ups.. Provides short-term coverage that can be removed with regular washing.. Helps keep hair feeling soft and smooth after application.. Blends well with existing hair color for an even appearance.. Convenient for travel, on-the-go use, or quick touch-ups.', 'Helps cover gray roots quickly for a natural-looking result.. Stick design allows precise and mess-free touch-ups..', 3.311, NULL, 'BHD', '["https://f.nooncdn.com/p/pzsku/Z3668A6CA14B051E7AC9DZ/45/_/1773515664/39d7fd0e-2d11-4003-841e-e1844c887233.jpg?width=1200","https://f.nooncdn.com/p/pzsku/Z3668A6CA14B051E7AC9DZ/45/_/1773515664/3c62beb5-71d6-4a0b-b7f4-8c07d287a690.jpg?width=1200","https://f.nooncdn.com/p/pzsku/Z3668A6CA14B051E7AC9DZ/45/_/1773515664/0da59077-4e00-402c-9532-a99e37d5bfe9.jpg?width=1200","https://f.nooncdn.com/p/pzsku/Z3668A6CA14B051E7AC9DZ/45/_/1773515664/dcb00731-9c95-446b-989d-f80f416bb537.jpg?width=1200"]'::jsonb, (select id from public.categories where slug = 'hair-color'), (select id from public.brands where slug = 'ikzee'), 3.7, 3, 0, true, false, true, ARRAY['hair', 'care', 'color', 'chemical', 'dyes']::text[]),
  ('Naturals Natural Black Argan Hair Color Shampoo – Fast Gray Hair Coverage in Just 8 Minutes with Nourishing Argan Oil Formula and Free Gloves – 400ml', 'naturals-natural-black-argan-hair-color-shampoo-fast-gray-hair-coverag', 'Get naturally black, shiny, and attractive hair easily with Naturals Argan Hair Color Shampoo. Its practical formula combines the convenience of shampoo with the effectiveness of hair color to provide fast gray hair coverage within minutes while caring for your hair with nourishing argan oil, known for its moisturizing and smoothing properties. The easy-to-use formula helps distribute color evenly for a natural-looking finish and softer, shinier hair without complicated steps. It also comes with free gloves for convenient home use. Key Features Effectively covers gray and white hair Natural black hair color Fast results in just 8 minutes Enriched with nourishing Argan Oil Helps leave hair soft and shiny Easy-to-use shampoo formula Even color distribution Suitable for home use Includes free gloves Benefits of Argan Oil for Hair Argan oil helps moisturize and improve the appearance of hair while adding softness and shine. It also helps reduce the appearance of dryness and frizz, leaving hair looking healthier and more vibrant. How to Use Wear the included gloves. Apply a suitable amount of shampoo to dry hair. Massage thoroughly to distribute the product evenly. Leave on for approximately 8 minutes. Rinse hair thoroughly with water until completely clean. Suitable For Men and women Hair with gray or white strands Quick and easy home use Anyone looking for fast gray hair coverage Product Details Brand: Naturals Product Type: Hair Color Shampoo Color: Natural Black Main Ingredient: Argan Oil Processing Time: 8 Minutes Size: 420ml Accessories: Free Gloves Included', 'Get naturally black, shiny, and attractive hair easily with Naturals Argan Hair Color Shampoo.', 2.7, NULL, 'BHD', '["https://f.nooncdn.com/p/pzsku/Z566ADDB5FCAD786E9EF1Z/45/_/1735